"Ranger\n"
"Druid\n"
"non-Chaotic aligned"
msgstr ""
"Lame du Chaos de Sarevok\n"
"Il s'agit de l'arme de Sarevok, frère de <CHARNAME>, qui fut utilisée dans la bataille de la Porte de Baldur. <CHARNAME> a gagné, ruinant ainsi les plans de Sarevok, et sauvant la Côte des Epées de la guerre. Maintenant, Sarevok s'est joint à la cause de <CHARNAME> et son épée lui a été rendue. Sarevok décrit cette arme comme une Lame Fatale et a restauré une partie des anciens pouvoirs de cet objet. Cependant, sans son essence d'Enfant de Bhaal pour nourrir l'épée, il n'a pu lui rendre la totalité du pouvoir qu'elle possédait autrefois. Quoiqu'il en soit, elle reste une arme formidable... et Sarevok prévient qu'elle deviendrait très difficile à utiliser dans les mains de quelqu'un qui ne fût pas un Porteur de Mort, voire impossible à utiliser.\n"
"\n"
"PARAMETRES :\n"
"\n"
"Capacités de combat : chaque coup porté draine de 1 à 5 points de vie de la cible et les transfère au porteur (qui ne peut pas dépasser son maximum).\n"
"\n"
"La lame procure également +10% de Résistance à la Magie lorsqu'elle est équipée.\n"
"\n"
"Dégâts : 1D10 +4\n"
"TAC0 : +4\n"
"Type de dégâts : tranchant\n"
"Poids : 10\n"
"Facteur de Vitesse : 8\n"
"Type de compétence : Epée à 2 mains\n"
"Type :  à 2 mains\n"
"Prérequis : 14 en Force, 18 en Constitution\n"
"Inutilisable par :\n"
"Clerc\n"
"Mage\n"
"Paladin\n"
"Rôdeur\n"
"Druide\n"
"Personnages d'alignement Non Chaotiques"

#: ascension.tra:3002
msgid "Sendai's Potion"
msgstr "Potion de Sendai"

#: ascension.tra:3003
msgid ""
"Sendai's Potion\n"
"Possibly a brew of Sendai's own, this is an incredibly potent healing potion capable of fully restoring the hit points of any who use it."
msgstr ""
"Potion de Sendai\n"
"Certainement confectionnée par Sendai elle-même, c'est une potion de soin d'une incroyable puissance capable de restaurer complètement les points de vie de celui qui la boit."

#: balth.tra:1060
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I wish I could take the credit for this ruse, <CHARNAME>.  But it seems I "
#| "was not the only member of the Five who plotted the downfall of the others."
msgid ""
"I wish I could take the credit for this ruse, <CHARNAME>. But it seems I was"
" not the only member of the Five who plotted the downfall of the others."
msgstr ""
"J'aimerais pouvoir revendiquer ce plan, <CHARNAME>, mais il semblerait que "
"je ne sois pas le seul membre de la Main à avoir comploter contre les "
"autres."

#: balth.tra:1072
msgid ""
"You won't be the first to try and kill me... and probably not the last!"
msgstr ""
"Vous ne serez pas le premier à essayer de me tuer... ni le dernier, à mon "
"avis !"

#: balth.tra:1074
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It is true.  You are a good <PRO_MANWOMAN>, <CHARNAME>, and your stance "
#| "against evil is without question.  Your fight against the taint of our evil "
#| "father is worthy of praise."
msgid ""
"It is true. You are a good <PRO_MANWOMAN>, <CHARNAME>, and your stance "
"against evil is without question. Your fight against the taint of our evil "
"father is worthy of praise."
msgstr ""
"C'est vrai. Vous êtes quelqu'un de doué, <CHARNAME>, et votre opposition au "
"mal est indiscutable. Votre combat contre la marque de votre père est "
"louable."

#: balth.tra:1075
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I sense no innate goodness within you, <CHARNAME>...though your deeds are "
#| "hailed far and wide as above reproach.  It is... interesting that one like "
#| "you who must struggle so much with our father's taint inside <PRO_HIMHER> "
#| "has done so much to fight true evil."
msgid ""
"I sense no innate goodness within you, <CHARNAME>...though your deeds are "
"hailed far and wide as above reproach. It is... interesting that one like "
"you who must struggle so much with our father's taint inside <PRO_HIMHER> "
"has done so much to fight true evil."
msgstr ""
"Je ne sens aucune bonté innée en vous, <CHARNAME>... bien que vos actes "
"soient réputés et hors de tous reproches. Il est... intéressant qu'une "
"personne comme vous qui soit tant marquée par l'essence de notre père ait "
"autant fait pour combattre le mal."

#: balth.tra:1076
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I see the good that is within you, <CHARNAME>, but your deeds are hardly "
#| "above reproach.  I sense only a soul that struggles with our father's taint,"
#| " that struggles to find the good path where none exists."
msgid ""
"I see the good that is within you, <CHARNAME>, but your deeds are hardly "
"above reproach. I sense only a soul that struggles with our father's taint, "
"that struggles to find the good path where none exists."
msgstr ""
"Je vois le bien en vous, <CHARNAME>, mais vos actes ne sont pas dénués de "
"reproches. Je sens une âme qui lutte avec la marque de notre père, qui lutte"
" pour trouver un bon chemin qui n'existe pas."

#: balth.tra:1077
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I sense no innate goodness within you, <CHARNAME>.  I do not think your "
#| "deeds above reproach.  I sense only a soul struggling against the taint of "
#| "<PRO_HISHER> father, much like mine own."
msgid ""
"I sense no innate goodness within you, <CHARNAME>. I do not think your deeds"
" above reproach. I sense only a soul struggling against the taint of "
"<PRO_HISHER> father, much like mine own."
msgstr ""
"Je ne sens aucune bonté innée en vous, <CHARNAME>. Je ne pense pas que vos "
"actes soient hors de tout reproche. Je sens une âme qui lutte avec la marque"
" de son père, un peu comme moi."

#: balth.tra:1078
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Actually, I am the perfect person to judge, <CHARNAME>.  I, too, contain the"
#| " taint of our father within me.  I, too, have felt its yearnings for blood, "
#| "its efforts to exert chaos upon my life.  I have mastered it... but only "
#| "barely.  Too well I know what it is capable of."
msgid ""
"Actually, I am the perfect person to judge, <CHARNAME>. I, too, contain the "
"taint of our father within me. I, too, have felt its yearnings for blood, "
"its efforts to exert chaos upon my life. I have mastered it... but only "
"barely. Too well I know what it is capable of."
msgstr ""
"En fait, je suis la personne parfaite pour juger, <CHARNAME>. Je possède moi"
" aussi la marque de notre père en moi. Moi aussi ai ressenti ses demandes de"
" sang, ses efforts pour apporter le chaos dans ma vie. Je l'ai dominé... "
"juste en surface. Je ne sais que trop bien de quoi cette force est capable."

#: balth.tra:1079
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Naturally.  Our taint brings us no peace, does it, <CHARNAME>?  We fight in "
#| "self-defense and yet still we kill, still we bring destruction.  We may "
#| "claim an absence of responsibility, should we desire, but I know all too "
#| "well what the taint in our soul is capable of.  Only barely do I keep it "
#| "mastered."
msgid ""
"Naturally. Our taint brings us no peace, does it, <CHARNAME>? We fight in "
"self-defense and yet still we kill, still we bring destruction. We may claim"
" an absence of responsibility, should we desire, but I know all too well "
"what the taint in our soul is capable of. Only barely do I keep it mastered."
msgstr ""
"Naturellement. Notre souillure ne nous apporte aucune paix, n'est-ce pas, "
"<CHARNAME> ? Nous nous battons pour nous défendre, et pourtant nous "
"continuons à tuer et à apporter la destruction. Nous pouvons excuser ceci en"
" disant que nous ne l'avons pas choisi, si nous le voulons, mais je sais "
"très bien de quoi cette force est capable. Je n'arrive qu'a exercer un "
"faible contrôle dessus."

#: balth.tra:1080
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I would expect no other response from a true <PRO_BROTHERSISTER> of mine.  I"
#| " know too well the thirst for death that comes with the taint of our sire.  "
#| "I have mastered it, but only barely... I pity those who are a slave to it."
msgid ""
"I would expect no other response from a true <PRO_BROTHERSISTER> of mine. I "
"know too well the thirst for death that comes with the taint of our sire. I "
"have mastered it, but only barely... I pity those who are a slave to it."
msgstr ""
"Je n'espérais pas d'autre réponse de la part d'un de mes parents. Je ne "
"connais que trop bien la soif de meurtre qui vient avec la souillure de "
"notre père. Je l'ai dominée, mais juste en surface... j'ai en pitié ceux qui"
" en sont devenus les esclaves."

#: balth.tra:1081
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do not make me laugh, <CHARNAME>.  If you expect me to believe that your "
#| "depraved existence exists to fight against evil in this world, then you "
#| "expect far too much."
msgid ""
"Do not make me laugh, <CHARNAME>. If you expect me to believe that the "
"reason for your depraved existence is to fight evil in this world, you "
"expect far too much."
msgstr ""
"Ne me faites pas rire, <CHARNAME>. Si vous pensez me convaincre que votre "
"misérable existence est consacrée à vaincre le mal dans ce monde, alors vous"
" vous faîtes des illusions."

#: balth.tra:1082
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But regardless of our wishes on the matter, our destiny has been written for"
#| " us, <CHARNAME>.  Some may run from it or deny it, while others embrace "
#| "it... but each and every Bhaalspawn has a seed within them that has sprung "
#| "forth a fruit laden with blood and murder.  Do you deny this?"
msgid ""
"But regardless of our wishes on the matter, our destiny has been written for"
" us, <CHARNAME>. Some may run from it or deny it, while others embrace it..."
" but each and every Bhaalspawn has a seed within them that has sprung forth "
"a fruit laden with blood and murder. Do you deny this?"
msgstr ""
"Mais en dehors de nos souhaits personnels, notre destinée est déjà écrite, "
"<CHARNAME>. Certains peuvent tenter de la fuir ou de la nier, tandis que "
"d'autres l'acceptent... mais chaque Enfant de Bhaal a une graine en lui qui "
"donne un fruit gorgé de sang et de meurtre. Niez-vous cela ?"

#: balth.tra:1083
msgid "Are you implying that you are somehow different, Balthazar?"
msgstr "Cherchez-vous à dire que vous êtes différent, Balthazar ?"

#: balth.tra:1084
msgid "I have only ever acted when it was necessary, in self-defense."
msgstr "J'ai seulement agi lorsque c'était nécessaire, pour me défendre."

#: balth.tra:1085
msgid ""
"You would make us out to be victims of circumstance rather than masters of "
"our own destiny."
msgstr ""
"Vous feriez de nous les victimes des circonstances plutôt que des maîtres de"
" notre destinée."

#: balth.tra:1086
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I deny nothing.  Death comes for all who stand in my way."
msgid "I deny nothing. Death comes for all who stand in my way."
msgstr ""
"Je ne nie rien. La mort vient à tous ceux qui se mettent en travers de ma "
"route."

#: balth.tra:1087
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am death incarnate, fool!  Not some weak fool wrapped in denial like "
#| "yourself!"
msgid ""
"I am death incarnate, fool! Not some weak fool wrapped in denial like "
"yourself!"
msgstr ""
"Je suis la mort incarnée, idiot ! Pas un quelconque imbécile enveloppé dans "
"sa dignité comme vous !"

#: balth.tra:1088
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have little doubt that you know whereof I speak.  The taint is strong "
#| "within you... stronger than any single other spawn of our sire that I have "
#| "seen.  You have felt the dreams, the urges, have you not?  The chaos that is"
#| " your destiny has ripped wantonly through your life, regardless of your "
#| "wishes, has it not?  Do you deny that you bring violence and destruction "
#| "wherever you go, <CHARNAME>?"
msgid ""
"I have little doubt that you know whereof I speak. The taint is strong "
"within you... stronger than any single other spawn of our sire that I have "
"seen. You have felt the dreams, the urges, have you not? The chaos that is "
"your destiny has ripped wantonly through your life, regardless of your "
"wishes, has it not? Do you deny that you bring violence and destruction "
"wherever you go, <CHARNAME>?"
msgstr ""
"Je pense que vous savez de quoi je parle. L'empreinte de Bhaal est forte en "
"vous... plus puissante que celle de n'importe quel Enfant que j'ai pu "
"rencontrer. Vous avez eu les rêves, ressenti l'envie de meurtre, non ? Le "
"chaos qu'est notre destinée s'est imposé dans votre vie, se moquant de vos "
"désirs, n'est-ce pas ? Niez-vous que vous apportez la violence et la "
"destruction où que vous alliez, <CHARNAME>?"

#: balth.tra:1089
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am nothing like you.  I exist to fight against the chaos of my taint, to "
#| "fight against the evil that Bhaal's legacy brings to this world.  I have "
#| "faced the evil within me and I have mastered it."
msgid ""
"I am nothing like you. I exist to fight against the chaos of my taint, to "
"fight against the evil that Bhaal's legacy brings to this world. I have "
"faced the evil within me and I have mastered it."
msgstr ""
"Je ne suis pas comme vous. J'existe pour combattre le chaos de mon âme, et "
"pour affronter le mal que l'héritage de Bhaal a apporté à ce monde. J'ai "
"fait face au mal en moi et je l'ai vaincu."

#: balth.tra:1090
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No.  I have brought my share of death and destruction to this land.  But I "
#| "see a larger purpose behind it... I seek to end the possibility of Bhaal's "
#| "return forever, and to wipe his taint from the land."
msgid ""
"No. I have brought my share of death and destruction to this land. But I see"
" a larger purpose behind it... I seek to end the possibility of Bhaal's "
"return forever, and to wipe his taint from the land."
msgstr ""
"Non. J'ai apporté ma part de mort et de destruction à cette contrée. Mais je"
" vois un plus grand but derrière ceci... je cherche à mettre fin à la "
"possibilité d'un retour de Bhaal à jamais, et détruire toute trace de sa "
"descendance."

#: balth.tra:1091
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have mastered the power within me and held the evil in check, but I know "
#| "as well... if not better... then most of my brethren the threat that it "
#| "holds for all of FaerÃ»n.  I will not allow this.  I have dedicated my life "
#| "to preventing it."
msgid ""
"I have mastered the power within me and held the evil in check, but I know "
"just as well... if not better... than most of my brethren the threat that it"
" holds for all of Faerun. I will not allow this. I have dedicated my life to"
" preventing it."
msgstr ""
"J'ai dominé le pouvoir qui était en moi, contrôlé le mal dans mon âme, mais "
"je sais aussi bien... non mieux... que n'importe lequel de mes parents, la "
"menace que cela fait peser sur l'ensemble de Féerune. Je ne permettrai pas "
"ceci. J'ai dédié ma vie à l'empêcher."

#: balth.tra:1092
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If only we had met under other circumstances, <CHARNAME>...I would have "
#| "liked to sit and compare the paths that have brought us to this point.  If "
#| "we had not been forced by destiny to bear this taint upon our souls, what "
#| "would have become of us?  I regret what I must do, yet I know it must be "
#| "done."
msgid ""
"If only we had met under other circumstances, <CHARNAME>...I would have "
"liked to sit and compare the paths that have brought us to this point. If we"
" had not been forced by destiny to bear this taint upon our souls, what "
"would have become of us? I regret what I must do, yet I know it must be "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Si seulement nous nous étions rencontrés en d'autres circonstances, "
"<CHARNAME>... J'aurais aimé discuter avec vous et comparer les chemins qui "
"nous ont amenés jusqu'ici. Si nous n'avions pas été forcés par notre "
"destinée de porter cette marque sur notre âme, que serait-il advenu de nous "
"? Je regrette ce que je dois faire, mais je sais que je n'ai pas le choix."

#: balth.tra:1093
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And what becomes of Melissan, then?  Is she free to raise Bhaal and complete"
#| " her plans?"
msgid ""
"And what becomes of Melissan, then? Is she free to raise Bhaal and complete "
"her plans?"
msgstr ""
"Et qu'adviendra-t-il de Mélissane, alors ? Sera-t-elle libre de ressusciter "
"Bhaal et d'achever ses plans ?"

#: balth.tra:1094
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You don't have to do this, Balthazar.  We don't have to fight each other."
msgid ""
"You don't have to do this, Balthazar. We don't have to fight each other."
msgstr ""
"Vous n'êtes pas obligé de faire ça, Balthazar. Nous n'avons pas forcément à "
"nous combattre."

#: balth.tra:1095
msgid ""
"You don't honestly see yourself as the force of righteousness in all this, "
"do you?"
msgstr ""
"Vous ne vous voyez quand même pas réellement comme une force de la justice "
"en agissant ainsi, non ?"

#: balth.tra:1096
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Enough talk, then.  Let's get this over with."
msgid "Enough talk, then. Let's get this over with."
msgstr "Assez parlé. Finissons-en."

#: balth.tra:1097
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Of course not.  It is she that holds the key to Bhaal's resurrection.  After"
#| " you are dead, she too must be destroyed."
msgid ""
"Of course not. It is she that holds the key to Bhaal's resurrection. After "
"you are dead, she too must be destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Bien sûr que non. C'est elle qui détient la clé pour la résurrection de "
"Bhaal. Après votre mort, elle devra être détruite."

#: balth.tra:1098
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then we should fight her together!  How do you know she still can't summon "
#| "Bhaal... everything you've fought for will be for nothing!"
msgid ""
"Then we should fight her together! How do you know she still can't summon "
"Bhaal... everything you've fought for will be for nothing!"
msgstr ""
"Alors nous devrions la combattre ensemble ! Comment pouvez-vous être sûr "
"qu'elle ne puisse pas déjà ressusciter Bhaal ? Dans ce cas là tout ce que "
"vous auriez fait n'aura servi à rien !"

#: balth.tra:1099
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And you're going to stop her alone?  Have you given any thought to the fact "
#| "that maybe you've been helping her all along, that she's been playing you "
#| "like a harp?"
msgid ""
"And you're going to stop her alone? Have you given any thought to the fact "
"that maybe you've been helping her all along, that she's been playing you "
"like a harp?"
msgstr ""
"Et vous pensez pouvoir la stopper seul ? Avez-vous réfléchi au fait que vous"
" l'ayez aidée tout du long, qu'elle s'est complètement jouée de vous ?"

#: balth.tra:1100
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yet another death added to your tally?  And what then, once you kill her?  "
#| "Once you have all that power and it's yours alone... you think you're going "
#| "to resist that?"
msgid ""
"Yet another death added to your tally? And what then, once you kill her? "
"Once you have all that power and it's yours alone... you think you're going "
"to resist that?"
msgstr ""
"Une mort de plus à ajouter à votre palmarès ? Et que ferez-vous ensuite, "
"quand elle sera morte ? Une fois que toute la puissance sera réunie en vous "
"seul... croyez-vous que vous pourrez y résister ?"

#: balth.tra:1101
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "What makes you think you could kill her?  I'm the one that has defeated all "
#| "the Bhaalspawn... while you were doing nothing but hiding in this fortress "
#| "making the peasants miserable."
msgid ""
"What makes you think you could kill her? I'm the one that has defeated all "
"the Bhaalspawn... while you were doing nothing but hiding in this fortress "
"making the peasants miserable."
msgstr ""
"Qu'est-ce qui vous fais croire que vous puissiez la tuer ? Je suis celui qui"
" a vaincu tous les autres Enfants de Bhaal... tandis que vous ne faisiez "
"rien d'autre que de vous cacher dans votre forteresse en rendant la vie des "
"paysans misérable."

#: balth.tra:1102
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I thought you were going to kill yourself after I was dead.  Sure you won't "
#| "see some more evil once Melissan is dead, too?  You'd probably make a "
#| "promising Lord of Murder, you know..."
msgid ""
"I thought you were going to kill yourself after I was dead. Sure you won't "
"see some more evil once Melissan is dead, too? You'd probably make a "
"promising Lord of Murder, you know..."
msgstr ""
"Je pensais que vous vous tueriez après que je sois mort. Et ainsi vous ne "
"verrez plus le mal une fois Mélissane morte, n'est-ce pas ? Hmmm, vous "
"feriez certainement un bon Seigneur du Meurtre..."

#: balth.tra:1103
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Forget it.  This is pointless.  Let's just get this over with."
msgid "Forget it. This is pointless. Let's just get this over with."
msgstr "Oubliez ça. C'est inutile."

#: balth.tra:1104
msgid "Fight her together?"
msgstr "L'affronter ensemble ?"

#: balth.tra:1105
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No.  How could I trust you?  What if we were to vanquish Melissan, I would "
#| "be weakened... you could end my life there and everything I have been "
#| "working towards will be for nothing."
msgid ""
"No. How could I trust you? What if we were to vanquish Melissan, I would be "
"weakened... you could end my life there and everything I have been working "
"towards will be for nothing."
msgstr ""
"Non. Comment pourrais-je vous croire ? Si nous parvenions à vaincre "
"Mélissane, je serais sûrement affaibli... vous pourriez mettre fin à ma vie "
"là-bas et tout ce pourquoi j'ai lutté serait perdu."

#: balth.tra:1106
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I had thought when this moment arrived, I would hold clearly to my purpose."
#| "  We must... end this, <CHARNAME>.  I wish this to be over with, one way or "
#| "the other."
msgid ""
"I had thought when this moment arrived, I would hold clearly to my purpose. "
"We must... end this, <CHARNAME>. I wish this to be over with, one way or the"
" other."
msgstr ""
"J'ai pensé que lorsque ce moment arriverait, je verrais clairement ce que je"
" dois faire. Nous devons... terminer ceci, <CHARNAME>. Je veux en finir avec"
" tout ça, d'une façon ou d'un autre."

#: balth.tra:1107
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Alright, Balthazar.  If that's what you want... let's end this now."
msgid "Alright, Balthazar. If that's what you want... let's end this now."
msgstr ""
"Très bien, Balthazar. Si c'est ce que vous voulez... finissons-en "
"maintenant."

#: balth.tra:1108
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am at a loss, <CHARNAME>.  You question me, and I have no good answers for"
#| " you.  My heart tells me that you must be killed, but I am not sure if I "
#| "should listen to it.  What... what would you have me do?"
msgid ""
"I am at a loss, <CHARNAME>. You question me, and I have no good answers for "
"you. My heart tells me that you must be killed, but I am not sure if I "
"should listen to it. What... what would you have me do?"
msgstr ""
"Je suis perdu, <CHARNAME>.  Vous me faîtes m'interroger et je n'ai aucune "
"bonne réponse à vous fournir. Mon coeur me dit que vous devez être tué, mais"
" je ne suis pas sûr que je devrais l'écouter. Que... que voudriez-vous que "
"je fasse ?"

#: balth.tra:1109
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Join me, Balthazar.  Let us fight Melissan together, instead of doing what "
#| "she wants us to."
msgid ""
"Join me, Balthazar. Let us fight Melissan together, instead of doing what "
"she wants us to."
msgstr ""
"Rejoignez-moi, Balthazar. Combattons Mélissane ensemble, au lieu de suivre "
"son jeu."

#: balth.tra:1110
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I don't know, Balthazar.  But I don't want to fight you."
msgid "I don't know, Balthazar. But I don't want to fight you."
msgstr "Je ne sais pas, Balthazar. Mais je ne veux pas vous combattre."

#: balth.tra:1111
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Let us fight, then, if it must be.  Let me give you some peace at last."
msgid "Let us fight, then, if it must be. Let me give you some peace at last."
msgstr ""
"Combattons alors, si ça doit être ainsi. Laissez-moi vous apporter un peu de"
" paix finalement."

#: balth.tra:1112
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You're a weaker fool then I thought.  Let's just end this now, shall we?  I "
#| "have an appointment with god-hood."
msgid ""
"You're a bigger fool than I thought. Let's just end this now, shall we? I "
"have an appointment with god-hood."
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes un imbécile plus faible que je ne le pensais. Finissons-en "
"maintenant, qu'en dites-vous ? J'ai un rendez-vous avec ma Déité."

#: balth.tra:1113
msgid "Yes... you are right."
msgstr "Oui... vous avez raison."

#: balth.tra:1114
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Very well, then, <CHARNAME>.  I will join you.  You are a worthy "
#| "<PRO_MANWOMAN>.  Perhaps even worthy of turning Bhaal's dark taint and "
#| "making something better of it.  I do not know.  But I will take that chance."
msgid ""
"Very well, then, <CHARNAME>. I will join you. You are a worthy "
"<PRO_MANWOMAN>. Perhaps even worthy of turning Bhaal's dark taint and making"
" something better of it. I do not know. But I will take that chance."
msgstr ""
"Très bien alors, <CHARNAME>. Je vais me joindre à vous. Vous êtes une "
"personne de valeur. Peut-être encore plus valeureuse par le fait de réussir "
"à dévier l'essence maléfique de Bhaal et vous en servir pour le bien. Je ne "
"suis pas certain que je prends la bonne décision. Mais je vais saisir cette "
"chance."

#: balth.tra:1115
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Let Melissan tremble when she sees us together, and we shall strike her down"
#| " as she deserves.  Even if Bhaal himself is resurrected, he will not be able"
#| " to hold out against us both.  I have preparations to make, <CHARNAME>.  Go "
#| "to the Throne of Bhaal.  When the time comes, I will be there."
msgid ""
"Let Melissan tremble when she sees us together, and we shall strike her down"
" as she deserves. Even if Bhaal himself is resurrected, he will not be able "
"to hold out against us both. I have preparations to make, <CHARNAME>. Go to "
"the Throne of Bhaal. When the time comes, I will be there."
msgstr ""
"Faisons trembler Mélissane quand elle nous verra tous deux, et démolissons-"
"la comme elle le mérite. Même si Bhaal lui-même est ressuscité, il ne sera "
"pas capable de tenir face à nous. Je dois me préparer, <CHARNAME>. Allez au "
"trône de Bhaal. Quand le temps viendra, je serai là."

#: balth.tra:1116
msgid "I cannot, <CHARNAME>."
msgstr "Je ne peux pas, <CHARNAME>."

#: balth.tra:1117
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You must take the battle to Melissan.  It is your destiny to see that "
#| "Bhaal's legacy ends here and now.  But you must promise me, <CHARNAME>...you"
#| " must promise me that you will not give into the temptation.  Should you "
#| "defeat Melissan and the power become available to you, you must turn away "
#| "from it... you have seen your struggle as it is now, with only a sliver of "
#| "that taint.  Do not take it, <CHARNAME>...even a god can be tempted, you "
#| "must realize that.  Promise me you will turn it away."
msgid ""
"You must take the battle to Melissan. It is your destiny to see that Bhaal's"
" legacy ends here and now. But you must promise me, <CHARNAME>...you must "
"promise me that you will not give into the temptation. Should you defeat "
"Melissan and the power become available to you, you must turn away from "
"it... you have seen your struggle as it is now, with only a sliver of that "
"taint. Do not take it, <CHARNAME>...even a god can be tempted, you must "
"realize that. Promise me you will turn it away."
msgstr ""
"Vous devez mener le combat contre Mélissane. C'est votre destinée d'assister"
" à la fin de l'héritage de Bhaal. Mais promettez-moi, <CHARNAME>... vous "
"devez me promettre de ne pas céder à la tentation. Si vous deviez vaincre "
"Mélissane et que ce pouvoir s'offrait à vous, détournez-vous en... Vous avez"
" vu ce qu'est votre lutte actuelle avec juste un soupçon de cette marque. Ne"
" le prenez pas, <CHARNAME>... même un Dieu peut être tenté, sachez ceci. "
"Promettez-moi de laisser cette puissance."

#: balth.tra:1118
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If I am given the option, Balthazar... I will refuse the taint.  I swear it."
msgid ""
"If I am given the option, Balthazar... I will refuse the taint. I swear it."
msgstr ""
"Si j'en ai l'option, Balthazar... je refuserai cet héritage. Je le jure."

#: balth.tra:1119
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No.  I will swear nothing of the kind.  Great good could come out of that "
#| "power, you don't know otherwise any better than I."
msgid ""
"No. I will swear nothing of the kind. Great good could come out of that "
"power, you don't know otherwise any better than I."
msgstr ""
"Non. Je ne permettrai rien de ce genre. Un grand bien peut résulter de cette"
" puissance, nul ne le sait mieux que moi."

#: balth.tra:1120
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Forget it!  I'll do no such thing!"
msgid "Forget it! I'll do no such thing!"
msgstr "Oubliez ça ! Je ne ferai pas une telle chose !"

#: balth.tra:1121
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then I am satisfied.  The essence of our sire ends with me... and with you."
#| "  May the gods forgive me.  May you... may you forgive me, "
#| "<PRO_BROTHERSISTER>..."
msgid ""
"Then I am satisfied. The essence of our sire ends with me... and with you. "
"May the gods forgive me. May you... may you forgive me, "
"<PRO_BROTHERSISTER>..."
msgstr ""
"Je suis satisfait. L'essence de notre Seigneur se termine avec moi... et "
"avec vous. Puissent les dieux me pardonner. Puissiez-vous... puissiez-vous "
"m'excuser, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>..."

#: balth.tra:1122
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then we must do battle.  I... I am sorry, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>.  I had hoped "
#| "this would be otherwise."
msgid ""
"Then we must do battle. I... I am sorry, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>. I had hoped "
"this would be otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Alors nous devrons nous battre. Je... je suis désolé, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>. "
"J'avais espéré qu'il en serait autrement."

#: balth.tra:1123
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And I cannot trust that you will turn aside the power when it is offered to "
#| "you.  You have experienced the struggle even a sliver of Bhaal's taint has "
#| "brought you, yet I cannot believe that you would turn it aside.  I... I am "
#| "sorry, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>...but I have no choice."
msgid ""
"And I cannot trust that you will turn aside the power when it is offered to "
"you. You have experienced the struggle even a sliver of Bhaal's taint has "
"brought you, yet I cannot believe that you would turn it aside. I... I am "
"sorry, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>...but I have no choice."
msgstr ""
"Et je ne peux croire que vous tournerez le dos au pouvoir qui s'offrira à "
"vous. Vous avez fait l'expérience de la lutte que seul un soupçon de "
"l'Essence de Bhaal vous apporte, pourtant je ne peux croire que vous vous en"
" détournerez. Je... je suis désolé, <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>... mais je n'ai pas "
"le choix."

#: balth.tra:1124
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "So be it.  Come, my pupils... may the gods help us all."
msgid "So be it. Come, my pupils... may the gods help us all."
msgstr "Ainsi soit-il. Venez mes élèves, puissent les Dieux nous aider."

#: balth.tra:1125
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No.  Further dialogue is pointless.  Let us end this now, <CHARNAME>...and "
#| "may the gods have pity on us all."
msgid ""
"No. Further dialogue is pointless. Let us end this now, <CHARNAME>...and may"
" the gods have pity on us all."
msgstr ""
"Non. Continuer de discuter est inutile. Terminons en maintenant, "
"<CHARNAME>... et puissent les dieux avoir pitié de nous."

#: balth.tra:1126
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps what you are saying holds merit.  But what if I died during the "
#| "battle?  What if I was weakened, in the end... you might find yourself... "
#| "tempted.  How could I trust you?"
msgid ""
"Perhaps what you are saying holds merit. But what if I died during the "
"battle? What if I was weakened, in the end... you might find yourself... "
"tempted. How could I trust you?"
msgstr ""
"Peut-être que ce que vous dites mérite d'être écouté. Mais et si je meurs "
"pendant le combat ? Si je me retrouve affaibli à la fin... vous pourriez "
"alors être tenté. Comment puis-je vous croire ?"

#: balth.tra:1128
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I don't know how to explain it, exactly, but she must have used you!  She "
#| "used everyone else!  I didn't trust her and she even got me to do what she "
#| "wanted!"
msgid ""
"I don't know how to explain it, exactly, but she must have used you! She "
"used everyone else! I didn't trust her and she even got me to do what she "
"wanted!"
msgstr ""
"Je ne sais pas comment l'expliquer exactement mais elle a dû vous utiliser !"
" Elle se sert de tout le monde ! Je ne lui faisait pas confiance et pourtant"
" elle a réussi à me faire faire ce qu'elle voulait !"

#: balth.tra:1129
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Think about it, Balthazar!  You honestly think she didn't know what your "
#| "plans were?  Do you think you took her by surprise?  Even I saw it coming, "
#| "and there was nothing I could do to stop it!"
msgid ""
"Think about it, Balthazar! You honestly think she didn't know what your "
"plans were? Do you think you took her by surprise? Even I saw it coming, and"
" there was nothing I could do to stop it!"
msgstr ""
"Pensez-y, Balthazar ! Vous croyez sincèrement qu'elle ne se doutait pas de "
"vos plans ici ? Vous imaginiez la prendre par surprise ? Même moi je l'ai "
"vue venir et il n'y a rien que je n'ai pu faire pour stopper ceci !"

#: balth.tra:1130
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "She used you to get rid of the other Bhaalspawn, obviously.  Think about it!"
#| "  She knew what you were planning all along.  She wanted all the Bhaalspawn "
#| "dead... and she wants us to fight!  She *wants* this to happen!!"
msgid ""
"She used you to get rid of the other Bhaalspawn, obviously. Think about it! "
"She knew what you were planning all along. She wanted all the Bhaalspawn "
"dead... and she wants us to fight! She *wants* this to happen!"
msgstr ""
"Elle s'est servie de vous pour se débarrasser des autres Enfants de Bhaal de"
" toute évidence. Pensez-y ! Elle savait depuis le début ce que vous vouliez "
"faire. Elle voulait voir tous les Enfants de Bhaal morts... et maintenant "
"elle veut que nous nous combattions ! Elle VEUX que ceci arrive !!"

#: balth.tra:1131
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Of course she used me, <CHARNAME>.  And no doubt she knew my plans as well "
#| "as I knew hers.  This changes nothing."
msgid ""
"Of course she used me, <CHARNAME>. And no doubt she knew my plans as well as"
" I knew hers. This changes nothing."
msgstr ""
"Bien sûr qu'elle s'est servie de moi, <CHARNAME>. Et il n'y a aucun doute "
"sur le fait qu'elle connaissait mes plans, tout comme je connaissais les "
"siens. Ca ne change rien."

#: balth.tra:1132
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You... may be right, <CHARNAME>.  But that does not mean that my plan will "
#| "fail.  Melissan underestimates me, I am sure of that... just as she "
#| "underestimates you."
msgid ""
"You... may be right, <CHARNAME>. But that does not mean that my plan will "
"fail. Melissan underestimates me, I am sure of that... just as she "
"underestimates you."
msgstr ""
"Vous... avez peut-être raison, <CHARNAME>. Mais ça ne veut pas dire que mon "
"plan va échouer. Mélissane me sous-estime j'en suis certain... tout comme "
"elle vous sous-estime."

#: balth.tra:1133
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I... perhaps you are right, <CHARNAME>.  I see the wisdom of your words.  "
#| "Still... this does not mean my plan is doomed to failure.  Or is it?"
msgid ""
"I... perhaps you are right, <CHARNAME>. I see the wisdom of your words. "
"Still... this does not mean my plan is doomed to failure. Or is it?"
msgstr ""
"Je... peut-être avez-vous raison, <CHARNAME>. Je vois la sagesse dans vos "
"mots. Pourtant... ça ne signifie pas que mon plan soit voué à l'échec, non ?"

#: balth.tra:1134
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I must resist it.  I will.  I have no choice."
msgid "I must resist it. I will. I have no choice."
msgstr "Je dois y résister. Je n'ai pas le choix."

#: balth.tra:1135
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But... you have shown great willpower, as well.  Despite the taint in your "
#| "soul, you have struggled against it just as I have.  What makes me more "
#| "worthy...?  No, I must not question myself!  Not now!"
msgid ""
"But... you have shown great willpower, as well. Despite the taint in your "
"soul, you have struggled against it just as I have. What makes me more "
"worthy...? No, I must not question myself! Not now!"
msgstr ""
"Mais... vous avez fait preuve d'une grande volonté également. En dépit de la"
" souillure de votre âme, vous avez lutté contre, tout comme moi. Qu'est-ce "
"qui me rendrait plus valeureux... ? Non, je ne dois pas m'interroger, pas "
"maintenant !"

#: balth.tra:1136
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You are certainly no better a candidate for resisting such temptation, "
#| "<CHARNAME>.  I would trust myself far more than I would trust you.  To send "
#| "you to the Throne would be to give up everything I have believed in."
msgid ""
"You are certainly no better a candidate for resisting such temptation, "
"<CHARNAME>. I would trust myself far more than I would trust you. To send "
"you to the Throne would be to give up everything I have believed in."
msgstr ""
"Vous n'êtes certainement pas un meilleur candidat pour résister à une telle "
"tentation, <CHARNAME>. J'ai davantage confiance en mon jugement qu'en le "
"vôtre. Vous laisser aller au Trône reviendrait à abandonner tout ce que en "
"quoi je crois."

#: balth.tra:1137
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Strength is nothing, <CHARNAME>.  You may vanquish me with your might, and "
#| "you may even vanquish Melissan.  But you will never vanquish yourself.  "
#| "Might will bring you no peace... this I know.  And this is why I must be the"
#| " last."
msgid ""
"Strength is nothing, <CHARNAME>. You may vanquish me with your might, and "
"you may even vanquish Melissan. But you will never vanquish yourself. Might "
"will bring you no peace... this I know. And this is why I must be the last."
msgstr ""
"La force n'est rien, <CHARNAME>. Vous pouvez me vaincre avec ma puissance, "
"et vous pouvez même vaincre Mélissane. Mais vous ne viendrez jamais à bout "
"de vous-même. La force ne vous apportera aucune paix... je le sais. Et c'est"
" pourquoi je dois être le dernier."

#: balth.tra:1138
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am tired of the battles I have fought, <CHARNAME>.  I am tired of the "
#| "anguish that I have endured, placing the greater good above the welfare of "
#| "others, of myself and my own immortal soul.  It will be enough that Bhaal's "
#| "legacy is destroyed, there is no temptation beyond that."
msgid ""
"I am tired of the battles I have fought, <CHARNAME>. I am tired of the "
"anguish that I have endured, placing the greater good above the welfare of "
"others, of myself and my own immortal soul. It will be enough that Bhaal's "
"legacy is destroyed, there is no temptation beyond that."
msgstr ""
"Je suis fatigué de tous les combats que j'ai menés, <CHARNAME>. Je suis "
"fatigué du tourment que j'ai enduré, plaçant le bien suprême au dessus du "
"bien des autres, de moi-même et de mon âme immortelle. Ce sera très bien si "
"l'héritage de Bhaal est détruit, sans tentation derrière."

#: balth.tra:1139
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "But I do.  It is my destiny.  What other choice have I?"
msgid "But I do. It is my destiny. What other choice have I?"
msgstr "Mais je le ferai. C'est ma destinée. Quel autre choix ai-je ?"

#: balth.tra:1140
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You always have a choice, Balthazar.  Don't be a slave to Alaundo's "
#| "prophecy!  I have fought against it ever since I found out about my heritage"
#| " and I will *not* give up!"
msgid ""
"You always have a choice, Balthazar. Don't be a slave to Alaundo's prophecy!"
" I have fought against it ever since I found out about my heritage and I "
"will *not* give up!"
msgstr ""
"Vous avez toujours le choix, Balthazar. Ne soyez pas un esclave de la "
"prophétie d' Alaundo ! Je l'ai combattue depuis que j'ai découvert mon "
"héritage et je n'abandonnerai pas !"

#: balth.tra:1141
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Alaundo's prophecy does not mean the Bhaalspawn must be destroyers, "
#| "Balthazar!  It also means we can stop the prophecy from becoming true, I "
#| "know this!"
msgid ""
"Alaundo's prophecy does not mean the Bhaalspawn must be destroyers, "
"Balthazar! It also means we can stop the prophecy from becoming true, I know"
" this!"
msgstr ""
"La prophétie d'Alaundo ne dit pas que les Enfants de Bhaal doivent être "
"détruits, Balthazar ! Ca veut aussi dire que nous pouvons empêcher la "
"prophétie de se réaliser, je le sais !"

#: balth.tra:1142
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You can walk away.  You can do what's right, Balthazar, what you know to be "
#| "right instead of what you've resigned yourself to."
msgid ""
"You can walk away. You can do what's right, Balthazar, what you know to be "
"right instead of what you've resigned yourself to."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez laisser tomber. Vous pouvez faire ce qui est bien, Balthazar, ce"
" que vous savez être bien au plus profond de vous, au lieu de faire ce à "
"quoi vous vous êtes résigné."

#: balth.tra:1143
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You are walking a path that you don't need to, Balthazar.  You see yourself "
#| "as evil, but it doesn't have to be that way."
msgid ""
"You are walking a path that you don't need to, Balthazar. You see yourself "
"as evil, but it doesn't have to be that way."
msgstr ""
"Vous suivez un chemin qui n'est pas le vôtre, Balthazar. Vous vous voyez "
"comme mauvais, mais ce n'est pas forcément ainsi."

#: balth.tra:1144
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am your <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, Balthazar.  Let us fight what is inevitable!"
#| "  We can work together!"
msgid ""
"I am your <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, Balthazar. Let us fight what is inevitable! "
"We can work together!"
msgstr ""
"Je suis votre <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, Balthazar. Combattons ce qui semble "
"inévitable ! Nous pouvons coopérer !"

#: balth.tra:1145
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Forget it.  There's no point in discussing this with you, is there?  Let's "
#| "get this over with."
msgid ""
"Forget it. There's no point in discussing this with you, is there? Let's get"
" this over with."
msgstr ""
"Oubliez ça. Il n'y a aucun intérêt à discuter de ça avec vous, n'est-ce pas "
"?"

#: balth.tra:1146
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You are impressive with your words, <CHARNAME>.  I can feel destiny altering"
#| " to your will, how you are the center of it all... how is it that I did not "
#| "see this before?"
msgid ""
"You are impressive with your words, <CHARNAME>. I can feel destiny altering "
"to your will, how you are the center of it all... how is it that I did not "
"see this before?"
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes doué avec les mots, <CHARNAME>. Je peux sentir la destinée "
"s'altérer selon votre volonté, de quelle façon vous êtes le centre de tout "
"ceci... comment n'ai-je pas pu voir cela plus tôt ?"

#: balth.tra:1147
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But the simple truth is your words ring hollow to me.  I do not believe "
#| "them.  You have fought against destiny, yet I see it in you even the more as"
#| " you speak."
msgid ""
"But the simple truth is your words ring hollow to me. I do not believe them."
" You have fought against destiny, yet I see it in you even the more as you "
"speak."
msgstr ""
"Mais la vérité simple de vos mots sonne comme un vide pour moi. Je ne les "
"crois pas. Vous avez combattu la destinée, mais je lis en vous comme dans un"
" livre ouvert."

#: balth.tra:1148
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps... perhaps there is something to your words.  I look within myself "
#| "and see how rigidly I have held myself to my destiny... and I feel hollow.  "
#| "But I... cannot believe that this has been for nothing."
msgid ""
"Perhaps... perhaps there is something to your words. I look within myself "
"and see how rigidly I have held myself to my destiny... and I feel hollow. "
"But I... cannot believe that this has been for nothing."
msgstr ""
"Peut-être... peut-être qu'il y a quelque chose dans vos paroles. Je regarde "
"en moi et vois de quelle façon rigide j'ai suivi mon destin... et je me sens"
" vide. Mais je... ne peux croire que tout cela ait été réalisé en vain."

#: balth.tra:1149
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "What do you mean?  How do you know this?"
msgid "What do you mean? How do you know this?"
msgstr "Que voulez-vous dire ? Comment savez-vous ceci ?"

#: balth.tra:1150
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It was told to me by a Solar, an agent of prophecy!  It... oh, I know how it"
#| " sounds, but it's true!"
msgid ""
"It was told to me by a Solar, an agent of prophecy! It... oh, I know how it "
"sounds, but it's true!"
msgstr ""
"Cela m'a été révélé par un Solaire, un agent de la prophétie ! Elle... oh, "
"je sais que ça a l'air étrange, mais c'est vrai !"

#: balth.tra:1151
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have been told many things by agents of Alaundo's prophecy... higher "
#| "beings that have sought me out to prepare me.  Alaundo's prophecy does not "
#| "necessarily mean what you think it does, Balthazar."
msgid ""
"I have been told many things by agents of Alaundo's prophecy... higher "
"beings that have sought me out to prepare me. Alaundo's prophecy does not "
"necessarily mean what you think it does, Balthazar."
msgstr ""
"J'ai appris beaucoup de choses par les agents de la prophétie d' Alaundo... "
"des êtres supérieurs qui m'ont cherché pour me préparer. La prophétie "
"d'Alaundo ne signifie pas nécessairement ce que vous croyez, Balthazar."

#: balth.tra:1152
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "A Solar has been my mentor since this began, guiding me and preparing me for"
#| " what is to come.  The prophecy is not so simple as you think it to be, no "
#| "matter how we assume it to be.  Think about it and you'll know it to be "
#| "true, Balthazar... everything has more than one side."
msgid ""
"A Solar has been my mentor since this began, guiding me and preparing me for"
" what is to come. The prophecy is not so simple as you think it to be, no "
"matter how we assume it to be. Think about it and you'll know it to be true,"
" Balthazar... everything has more than one side."
msgstr ""
"Un Solaire a été mon mentor depuis que tout ceci a commencé, me guidant et "
"me préparant à ce qui allait arriver. La prophétie n'est pas aussi simple "
"que vous l'imaginez, quoi que nous puissions en penser. Réfléchissez-y et "
"vous saurez que c'est vrai, Balthazar... chaque chose a plus d'une face."

#: balth.tra:1153
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have no agent of the heavens to interpret my destiny for me, <CHARNAME>.  "
#| "And my path remains clear."
msgid ""
"I have no agent of the heavens to interpret my destiny for me, <CHARNAME>. "
"And my path remains clear."
msgstr ""
"Je n'ai pas d'agent dans les cieux pour interpréter ma destinée à ma place, "
"<CHARNAME>. Et mon chemin reste clair."

#: balth.tra:1154
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You plant a seed of doubt in me, <CHARNAME>, and I begin to wonder.  Yet... "
#| "it seems that my destiny may differ from yours.  I have no heavenly "
#| "guidance.  Perhaps my path has been made for me, yet."
msgid ""
"You plant a seed of doubt in me, <CHARNAME>, and I begin to wonder. Yet... "
"it seems that my destiny may differ from yours. I have no heavenly guidance."
" Perhaps my path has been made for me, yet."
msgstr ""
"Vous semez le doute en moi, <CHARNAME>, et je commence à m'interroger. "
"Pourtant... il semble que ma destinée diffère de la votre. Je n'ai pas de "
"guide divin. Peut-être que mon chemin a déjà été tracé pour moi."

#: balth.tra:1155
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "What you say is incredible, and yet... it does make sense.  Have I prepared "
#| "myself for all this time in error?  How could this be?"
msgid ""
"What you say is incredible, and yet... it does make sense. Have I prepared "
"myself for all this time in error? How could this be?"
msgstr ""
"Ce que vous dites est incroyable, et pourtant... c'est sensé. Me suis-je "
"conforté tout ce temps dans l'erreur ? Comment est-ce possible ?"

#: balth.tra:1156
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "An appealing notion, to walk away.  Would that I could do so.  Would that "
#| "any of us could have done so."
msgid ""
"An appealing notion, to walk away. Would that I could do so. Would that any "
"of us could have done so."
msgstr ""
"Une idée intéressante, pour fuir. Je pourrais en faire autant. N'importe "
"lequel d'entre nous aurait pu en faire autant."

#: balth.tra:1157
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But perhaps I have resigned myself to a path that is not what it seems.  You"
#| " are... hardly what I expected for the last of the Bhaalspawn, <CHARNAME>.  "
#| "Perhaps there is hope... or perhaps I am only deluding myself."
msgid ""
"But perhaps I have resigned myself to a path that is not what it seems. You "
"are... hardly what I expected for the last of the Bhaalspawn, <CHARNAME>. "
"Perhaps there is hope... or perhaps I am only deluding myself."
msgstr ""
"Mais peut-être que je me suis résigné à suivre un chemin qui n'est pas ce "
"qu'il semble être. Vous ne ressemblez pas vraiment à ce à quoi je "
"m'attendais de la part du dernier Enfant de Bhaal, <CHARNAME>. Peut-être "
"qu'il y a de l'espoir... ou peut-être suis-je en train de me bercer "
"d'illusions."

#: balth.tra:1158
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But that is a fool's notion, <CHARNAME>, and I am no fool.  There is no such"
#| " option available to me or any of us, no matter how appealing you may make "
#| "it seem."
msgid ""
"But that is a fool's notion, <CHARNAME>, and I am no fool. There is no such "
"option available to me or any of us, no matter how appealing you may make it"
" seem."
msgstr ""
"Mais c'est une notion stupide, <CHARNAME>, et je ne suis pas idiot. Il n'y a"
" pas de telle option qui nous soit disponible, même si vous voulez me faire "
"croire le contraire."

#: balth.tra:1159
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No!  You have listened to nothing I have said!  It *is* that way because "
#| "there is no choice for us!  You would have me forget all the murders I have "
#| "committed with my own hands, all the wrongs I have done in the name of the "
#| "greater good... I cannot forget!  I will not forgive myself and I will *not*"
#| " allow others to be afflicted with the taint I possess!"
msgid ""
"No! You have listened to nothing I have said! It *is* that way because there"
" is no choice for us! You would have me forget all the murders I have "
"committed with my own hands, all the wrongs I have done in the name of the "
"greater good... I cannot forget! I will not forgive myself and I will *not* "
"allow others to be afflicted with the taint I possess!"
msgstr ""
"Non ! Vous n'avez rien écouté de ce que j'ai dit ! C'est de cette façon car "
"il n'y a pas d'autre choix pour nous ! Vous voudriez me faire oublier tous "
"les meurtres que j'ai commis de ma main, toutes les fautes que j'ai commises"
" au nom du bien suprême...  je ne peux pas oublier ! Je ne me le "
"pardonnerais pas, et je ne laisserai pas les autres être affligés par le "
"même fardeau que moi !"

#: balth.tra:1160
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You have considerable charisma, <CHARNAME>...but it is because we are "
#| "siblings that we cannot work together.  You know as well as I what the "
#| "essence seeks, and it will not be satisfied until our destiny is culminated."
msgid ""
"You have considerable charisma, <CHARNAME>...but it is because we are "
"siblings that we cannot work together. You know as well as I what the "
"essence seeks, and it will not be satisfied until our destiny is culminated."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez un charisme considérable, <CHARNAME>... mais c'est parce que nous "
"sommes parents que nous ne pouvons nous unir. Vous savez aussi bien que moi "
"ce que veut cette essence, et je ne serai pas satisfait tant que notre "
"destinée ne sera pas réglée."

#: balth.tra:1161
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I make no judgement upon you, <CHARNAME>.  You are what you were born to be."
#| "  I can only trust myself to hold to the path of good that will lead to the "
#| "destruction of the true evil that threatens FaerÃ»n.  There is no other path"
#| " for me."
msgid ""
"I make no judgement upon you, <CHARNAME>. You are what you were born to be. "
"I can only trust myself to hold to the path of good that will lead to the "
"destruction of the true evil that threatens Faerun. There is no other path "
"for me."
msgstr ""
"Je ne vous juge pas, <CHARNAME>. Vous êtes tel que vous êtes né. Je peux "
"seulement croire que suivre le chemin du bien me permettra de détruire le "
"mal qui menace Féerune. Il n'y a pas de meilleure voie pour moi."

#: balth.tra:1162
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Look at the suffering you have brought to Amkethran!  Your monks terrorize "
#| "the innocent at your command!  You hire soulless mercenaries that cut down "
#| "the innocent at the slightest provocation!  And all for nothing!  You call "
#| "these the actions of a good man?"
msgid ""
"Look at the suffering you have brought to Amkethran! Your monks terrorize "
"the innocent at your command! You hire soulless mercenaries that cut down "
"the innocent at the slightest provocation! And all for nothing! You call "
"these the actions of a good man?"
msgstr ""
"Regardez la souffrance que vous avez amenée à Amkethran ! Vos moines "
"terrorisent les innocents en votre nom ! Vous engagez des mercenaires sans "
"coeur qui tuent les innocents à la moindre embrouille ! Et tout ça pour rien"
" ! Vous appellez ceci les actions d'un homme bon ?"

#: balth.tra:1163
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "A truly good man would have stood against Melissan from the beginning.  You "
#| "say you wanted to find out who the Five were... and yet I defeated them "
#| "without your scheming.  It was your choice to join the Five in their reign "
#| "of destruction, so live up to it!"
msgid ""
"A truly good man would have stood against Melissan from the beginning. You "
"say you wanted to find out who the Five were... and yet I defeated them "
"without your scheming. It was your choice to join the Five in their reign of"
" destruction, so live up to it!"
msgstr ""
"Un véritable homme de bien se serait opposé à Mélissane dès le début. Vous "
"dites que vous vouliez découvrir qui composait la Main... et pourtant je les"
" ai vaincus. C'était votre choix de les rejoindre dans leur règne de "
"destruction ! Vivez avec cela sur la conscience !"

#: balth.tra:1164
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You make no judgement upon me?  Don't make me laugh!  Inevitability is only "
#| "the newest excuse for yet one more murder!  You would make our father proud!"
msgid ""
"You make no judgement upon me? Don't make me laugh! Inevitability is only "
"the newest excuse for yet one more murder! You would make our father proud!"
msgstr ""
"Vous ne faites aucun jugement sur moi ? Ne me faites pas rire ! "
"L'inévitabilité n'est qu'une excuse supplémentaire pour un meurtre de plus !"
" Notre père serait fier de vous !"

#: balth.tra:1165
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And what if that is my path, too, Balthazar?  You say you don't judge me, "
#| "and yet you hold yourself to some duty as the only person who can fight "
#| "against evil?  Do you know destiny so well that you can say for certain "
#| "where it leads for someone else, never mind yourself?"
msgid ""
"And what if that is my path, too, Balthazar? You say you don't judge me, and"
" yet you hold yourself to some duty as the only person who can fight against"
" evil? Do you know destiny so well that you can say for certain where it "
"leads for someone else, never mind yourself?"
msgstr ""
"Et si nos chemins étaient identiques, Balthazar ? Vous dites que vous ne me "
"jugez pas, et pourtant vous vous maintenez tout seul à un devoir, comme si "
"vous étiez le seul à pouvoir lutter contre le mal ? Connaissez-vous si bien "
"la destinée pour pouvoir dire sans vous tromper où mène celle des autres ?"

#: balth.tra:1166
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Then let's get this over with.  I'm tired of talking."
msgid "Then let's get this over with. I'm tired of talking."
msgstr "Alors finissons-en. Je suis fatigué de discuter."

#: balth.tra:1167
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It... it is true.  I paid little attention to my men's actions, but I... I "
#| "knew what they were doing.  I thought it a great sacridice, necessary to "
#| "maintain secrecy, to attain my ultimate goal that they, in their ignorance, "
#| "did not know would benefit them more in the end.  But... it is how we treat "
#| "the most helpless of our brethren in the worst of times that marks the "
#| "goodness of a man, does it not?  I... I am ashamed, <CHARNAME>.  I sought..."
#| " only to do what was best for us all."
msgid ""
"It... it is true. I paid little attention to my men's actions, but I... I "
"knew what they were doing. I thought it a great sacrifice, necessary to "
"maintain secrecy, to attain my ultimate goal that they, in their ignorance, "
"did not know would benefit them more in the end. But... it is how we treat "
"the most helpless of our brethren in the worst of times that marks the "
"goodness of a man, does it not? I... I am ashamed, <CHARNAME>. I sought... "
"only to do what was best for us all."
msgstr ""
"C'est... c'est vrai. Je n'accorde que peu d'attention aux actions de mes "
"hommes, mais je... je savais ce qu'ils faisaient. Je pensais que c'était un "
"sacrifice nécessaire pour atteindre mon but, qui finirait par bénéficier à "
"tous. Mais... c'est la façon dont nous traitons nos compatriotes dans les "
"moments difficiles qui fait la grandeur d'un homme, non ? Je... je suis "
"honteux, <CHARNAME>. Je cherchais... seulement à faire ce qui était le mieux"
" pour tous."

#: balth.tra:1168
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You found out who the Five were through Melissan's scheming... and through, "
#| "in no small part, my own.  But who is to say that things might not have been"
#| " different?  Who are *you* to say that things might have been different?"
msgid ""
"You found out who the Five were through Melissan's scheming... and through, "
"in no small part, my own. But who is to say that things might not have been "
"different? Who are *you* to say that things might have been different?"
msgstr ""
"Vous avez découvert qui composait la Main à travers les plans de "
"Mélissane... et, qui plus est vous m'avez trouvé. Mais qui peux dire que les"
" choses auraient pu être différentes ? Qui êtes-vous pour affirmer cela ?"

#: balth.tra:1169
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But... it is true, nevertheless.  I have taken the easy path, and have done "
#| "much that has brought harm to others in the name of necessity.  But when "
#| "does 'necessity' cross into the realm of evil?  I... I am ashamed, "
#| "<CHARNAME>."
msgid ""
"But... it is true, nevertheless. I have taken the easy path, and have done "
"much that has brought harm to others in the name of necessity. But when does"
" 'necessity' cross into the realm of evil? I... I am ashamed, <CHARNAME>."
msgstr ""
"Mais... c'est vrai quoiqu'il en soit. J'ai choisi la voie la plus facile, et"
" cela a apporté beaucoup de souffrance au nom de la nécessité. Mais à partir"
" de quel moment cette nécessité croise-t-elle le chemin du mal ? J'ai... "
"j'ai honte, <CHARNAME>."

#: balth.tra:1170
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I do not stand here proud of my accomplishments in attaining what I see to "
#| "be a necessary goal... but neither should you.  You have blundered about, "
#| "causing more harm by your negligence than I ever could by my plotting."
msgid ""
"I do not stand here proud of my accomplishments in attaining what I see to "
"be a necessary goal... but neither should you. You have blundered about, "
"causing more harm by your negligence than I ever could by my plotting."
msgstr ""
"Je ne suis pas fier de ce que j'ai fait pour atteindre ce que je vois comme "
"un but nécessaire... mais il devrait en aller de même pour vous. Vous avez "
"causé autant de mal par votre négligence que moi à travers mes plans."

#: balth.tra:1171
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I will *not* be mocked so!  I have sacrificed my entire life, the people of "
#| "this village, everything I have in order to see this evil destroyed!  "
#| "Destroyed, all of it!  I cry out to Ao the Overfather that such evil must "
#| "not be allowed to live in the hearts of mortals, and I *will* be heard!"
msgid ""
"I will *not* be mocked so! I have sacrificed my entire life, the people of "
"this village, everything I have in order to see this evil destroyed! "
"Destroyed, all of it! I cry out to Ao the Overfather that such evil must not"
" be allowed to live in the hearts of mortals, and I *will* be heard!"
msgstr ""
"Je ne me laisserai pas humilier ainsi ! J'ai sacrifié ma vie entière, les "
"gens de ce village et tout ce que j'avais dans l'espoir de voir ce mal "
"détruit ! Complètement détruit ! J'hurle au grand Ao qu'un tel mal ne "
"devrait être autorisé à vivre dans le coeur des mortels, et je serai entendu"
" !"

#: balth.tra:1172
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I... know only what the temptations are that the taints puts upon us, "
#| "<CHARNAME>.  I know only that if our power was to grow, if your power was to"
#| " grow, that so would the temptation."
msgid ""
"I... know only what the temptations are that the taints puts upon us, "
"<CHARNAME>. I know only that if our power was to grow, if your power was to "
"grow, that so would the temptation."
msgstr ""
"Je... sais seulement que la tentation est liée à cet héritage, <CHARNAME>. "
"Je sais juste que si notre pouvoir grandit, si votre pouvoir grandit, alors "
"la tentation l'accompagnera."

#: balth.tra:1173
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But... you have been successful in fighting temptation.  More successful "
#| "than I.  I have... done much that I regret, in the name of good.  My people "
#| "suffer because I held my ultimate goal above all else... but is it not true "
#| "that our treatment of the least of our brethren is the true judge of a man's"
#| " soul?  I... I am ashamed."
msgid ""
"But... you have been successful in fighting temptation. More successful than"
" I. I have... done much that I regret, in the name of good. My people suffer"
" because I held my ultimate goal above all else... but is it not true that "
"our treatment of the least of our brethren is the true judge of a man's "
"soul? I... I am ashamed."
msgstr ""
"Mais... vous avez été victorieux dans votre combat contre la tentation. Plus"
" glorieux que moi. J'ai... causé tant de souffrance au nom du Bien. Mon "
"peuple souffre car je tiens mon but ultime au-dessus de tout... mais ne dit-"
"on pas que pour juger un homme il faut voir de quelle façon il traite les "
"plus pauvres que lui ? J'ai... j'ai honte."

#: balth.tra:1174
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And despite what you might profess, I think the taint sits closer to your "
#| "heart then you would have me believe.  I must walk my own path, "
#| "<CHARNAME>...and you must walk yours."
msgid ""
"And despite what you might profess, I think the taint sits closer to your "
"heart then you would have me believe. I must walk my own path, "
"<CHARNAME>...and you must walk yours."
msgstr ""
"Et en dépit de ce que vous pouvez dire, je pense que la marque de notre père"
" est plus proche de votre coeur que vous voulez bien me le faire croire. Je "
"dois suivre mon chemin, et vous le vôtre, <CHARNAME>."

#: balth.tra:1175
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Very well.  Come, my students... my teachings are ended.  We make our last "
#| "stand now for what is right.  May the gods have pity on us all."
msgid ""
"Very well. Come, my students... my teachings are ended. We make our last "
"stand now for what is right. May the gods have pity on us all."
msgstr ""
"Très bien. Venez mes étudiants... mes leçons sont terminées. Battons-nous "
"maintenant pour ce qui est bien. Puissent les dieux avoir pitié de nous "
"tous."

#: balth.tra:1176
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Even had destiny not brought us to this point, I doubt things would have "
#| "been different.  Perhaps if you had not borne the taint of our sire, things "
#| "might have been different with you.  I would have liked to meet a "
#| "<PRO_MANWOMAN> such as yourself without the taint on your soul, I think.  "
#| "But now I have little choice."
msgid ""
"Even had destiny not brought us to this point, I doubt things would have "
"been different. Perhaps if you had not borne the taint of our sire, things "
"might have been different with you. I would have liked to meet a "
"<PRO_MANWOMAN> such as yourself without the taint on your soul, I think. But"
" now I have little choice."
msgstr ""
"Même si la destinée ne nous avait amenés jusqu'ici, je doute que les choses "
"eussent été différentes. Peut-être que si vous n'étiez pas né avec cet "
"héritage, tout aurait pu se passer autrement. J'aurais aimé être ami avec "
"quelqu'un comme vous je pense, si il n'y avait ceci. Mais maintenant je n'ai"
" pas trop le choix."

#: balth.tra:1177
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Would that your claim of innocence meant anything to the dead of Saradush.  "
#| "Were I to question the recent dead of Athkatla, of Baldur's Gate, of "
#| "Candlekeep... would I not find some who would claim such innocence for "
#| "themselves?  Who died merely because they were caught in your wake?"
msgid ""
"Would that your claim of innocence meant anything to the dead of Saradush. "
"Were I to question the recent dead of Athkatla, of Baldur's Gate, of "
"Candlekeep... would I not find some who would claim such innocence for "
"themselves? Who died merely because they were caught in your wake?"
msgstr ""
"Croyez-vous que clamer votre innocence signifie quoi que ce soit pour les "
"morts de Saradush ? Même si je devais questionner les morts d'Athkatla, de "
"la Porte de Baldur ou de Châteausuif... ne trouverais-je pas autant de gens "
"criant leur propre innocence ? Combien sont morts juste parce qu'ils ont été"
" pris dans votre éveil ?"

#: balth.tra:1178
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do you think that others of our kind are any different?  Count them, "
#| "<CHARNAME>, and think of the multitudes of Bhaalspawn that existed and "
#| "brought misery to others, if not by intent, then even by their very "
#| "presence.  Would you allow such carnage to continue?  Have we not spared the"
#| " entire land from agony by the slaying of our siblings?"
msgid ""
"Do you think that others of our kind are any different? Count them, "
"<CHARNAME>, and think of the multitudes of Bhaalspawn that existed and "
"brought misery to others, if not by intent, then even by their very "
"presence. Would you allow such carnage to continue? Have we not spared the "
"entire land from agony by the slaying of our siblings?"
msgstr ""
"Pensez-vous que les autres de notre espèce sont différents ? Comptez-les, "
"<CHARNAME>, et pensez au nombre d'Enfants de Bhaal qui sont nés et qui ont "
"apporté la misère aux autres, même si ce n'était pas intentionnel, juste par"
" leur présence. Allez-vous permettre à un tel carnage de continuer ? "
"N'avons-nous pas assez plongé cette contrée dans la souffrance ?"

#: balth.tra:1179
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You believe yourself to be the master of your destiny, do you?  The destiny "
#| "foreseen long ago by Alaundo?  You believe it by choice alone that you ended"
#| " up here, in this place?"
msgid ""
"You believe yourself to be the master of your destiny, do you? The destiny "
"foreseen long ago by Alaundo? You believe it by choice alone that you ended "
"up here, in this place?"
msgstr ""
"Vous croyez être le maître de votre destinée, n'est-ce pas ? La destinée vue"
" il y a bien longtemps par Alaundo ? Vous pensez que c'est par choix "
"personnel que vous êtes arrivé là ?"

#: balth.tra:1180
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You mistake the path for the journey, my friend.  Whatever paths you have "
#| "taken since leaving Candlekeep, the journey has ended here as it was always "
#| "meant to.  Destiny masters us... we do not master it."
msgid ""
"You mistake the path for the journey, my friend. Whatever paths you have "
"taken since leaving Candlekeep, the journey has ended here as it was always "
"meant to. Destiny masters us... we do not master it."
msgstr ""
"Vous vous trompez sur le chemin de votre aventure, mon ami. Quelles que "
"soient les routes que vous ayez suivies depuis votre départ de Châteausuif, "
"l'histoire se termine ici comme si cela avait déjà été décidé. Le destin "
"nous contrôle... et non le contraire."

#: balth.tra:1181
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes, whether they were obstacles to be overcome or merely by-standers "
#| "crossing your path.  My own life has been little different, no matter how I "
#| "have struggled against it.  I am glad you see this... it will make things "
#| "much easier."
msgid ""
"Yes, whether they were obstacles to be overcome or merely by-standers "
"crossing your path. My own life has been little different, no matter how I "
"have struggled against it. I am glad you see this... it will make things "
"much easier."
msgstr ""
"Oui, quels que soient les obstacles à franchir ou les gens se mettant en "
"travers de notre chemin. Ma vie entière n'a guère été différente, bien que "
"j'ai énormément lutté contre. Je suis heureux que vous réalisiez cela, ça "
"rendra les choses plus faciles."

#: balth.tra:1182
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You sound like Yaga-Shura, a giant in ego as well as body.  Yet he fell, "
#| "too, when his fate came due.  The power of your blood may yet make you "
#| "victorious, it is true, but the fact that you embrace the taint within you "
#| "makes my own path that much the clearer."
msgid ""
"You sound like Yaga-Shura, a giant in ego as well as body. Yet he fell, too,"
" when his fate came due. The power of your blood may yet make you "
"victorious, it is true, but the fact that you embrace the taint within you "
"makes my own path that much the clearer."
msgstr ""
"Vous ressemblez à Yaga-Shura, aussi grand d'égo que de corps. Pourtant il "
"est tombé lui aussi, quand son heure est venue. La puissance de votre sang "
"peut vous rendre victorieux, certes, mais le fait que vous acceptez si bien "
"cette souillure me rend certain de ce que je dois faire."

#: balth_finsol.tra:580
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Only one other spawn of the dead god remains... the sibling who fought at "
#| "your side.  His portion of the essence is less than your own, but still "
#| "significant.  His choice must also be made."
msgid ""
"Only one other spawn of the dead god remains... the sibling who fought at "
"your side. His portion of the essence is less than your own, but still "
"significant. His choice must also be made."
msgstr ""
"Un seul autre enfant du Dieu mort subsiste... celui qui a combattu à ton "
"côté. Sa part d'essence divine est plus faible que la tienne, mais toujours "
"signifiante.  Son choix doit aussi être fait."

#: balth_finsol.tra:581
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "First, however, there is the matter of the children of the dead god who "
#| "fought by your side.  Their essences are less than your own, but their "
#| "decision no less important."
msgid ""
"First, however, there is the matter of the children of the dead god who "
"fought by your side. Their essences are less than your own, but their "
"decision no less important."
msgstr ""
"En premier lieu, il y a le problème des enfants du Dieu mort qui ont "
"combattu à tes côtés. Leurs essences divines sont plus faibles que la "
"tienne, mais leur décision n'en est pas moins importante."

#: balth_finsol.tra:582
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I am merely an agent of the universe in this matter, Balthazar.  I am "
#| "charged to see the destiny of the children of Bhaal brought to its "
#| "conclusion.  You have an opportunity that few are given.  You may choose "
#| "your destiny... a choice you thought yourself forever denied."
msgid ""
"I am merely an agent of the universe in this matter, Balthazar. I am charged"
" to see the destiny of the children of Bhaal brought to its conclusion. You "
"have an opportunity that few are given. You may choose your destiny... a "
"choice you thought yourself forever denied."
msgstr ""
"Je ne suis qu'un agent de l'univers dans cette affaire, Balthazar. Je suis "
"chargée de voir la destinée des Enfants de Bhaal portée à sa conclusion. Tu "
"as une opportunité que peu ont. Tu peux choisir ta destinée... un choix que "
"tu avais toujours crû t'être refusé."

#: balth_finsol.tra:583
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If that is your choice, you may surrender the portion of your divine essence"
#| " to your elder sibling.  You may become a normal mortal, with a destiny to "
