msgid ""
"If that is your choice, you may surrender the portion of your divine essence"
" to your elder sibling. You may become a normal mortal, with a destiny to "
"follow as you see fit."
msgstr ""
"Si tel est ton choix, tu pourrais donner cette portion de ton essence divine"
" à ton parent aîné. Tu pourrais devenir un simple mortel, avec un destin que"
" tu choisirais de mener selon ton gré."

#: balth_finsol.tra:584
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
