msgid ""
"And there is nothing that I ever wanted more. I choose to become a mortal "
"gladly, and with all my heart. To walk the earth without that dark burden "
"twisting my soul... I... I cannot even imagine..."
msgstr ""
"Et il n'y a rien que je ne souhaiterais plus. Je choisis de devenir un "
"mortel avec joie, et de tout mon coeur. Marcher sur terre sans ce sombre "
"fardeau tourmentant mon âme... je... je peux à peine l'imaginer..."

#: balth_finsol.tra:1012
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I cannot thank you enough, <CHARNAME>, for the gift you have given me.  I "
#| "once thought I had done everything I could to fight for what was good... but"
#| " it was you that showed me how wrong I was.  Without you, I would have died "
#| "with that stain upon my soul and perhaps even been Melissan's puppet "
#| "forever."
msgid ""
"I cannot thank you enough, <CHARNAME>, for the gift you have given me. I "
"once thought I had done everything I could to fight for what was good... but"
" it was you that showed me how wrong I was. Without you, I would have died "
"with that stain upon my soul and perhaps even been Melissan's puppet "
"forever."
msgstr ""
"Je ne peux assez vous remercier, <CHARNAME>, pour le cadeau que vous m'avez "
"fait. Je pensais avoir fait tout ce qui était possible pour préserver le "
"bien, mais c'est vous qui m'avez montré à quel point je me trompais. Sans "
"vous, je serais mort avec ce péché sur mon âme et peut-être été la "
"marionnette de Mélissane à jamais."

#: balth_finsol.tra:1013
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I cannot pretend to know what you are thinking, now, of the decision you "
#| "must make.  Nor do I pretend to certainty that the taint would bring such a "
#| "<PRO_MANWOMAN> such as yourself towards evil.  Perhaps you would overcome "
#| "that taint and be a good god, I cannot say."
msgid ""
"I cannot pretend to know what you are thinking, now, of the decision you "
"must make. Nor do I pretend to certainty that the taint would bring such a "
"<PRO_MANWOMAN> such as yourself towards evil. Perhaps you would overcome "
"that taint and be a good god, I cannot say."
msgstr ""
"Je ne peux prétendre savoir à quoi vous pensez en ce moment sur la décision "
"que vous devez prendre. Et je ne prétends pas non plus que l'héritage de "
"Bhaal conduirait quelqu'un de votre valeur vers le mal. Peut-être "
"parviendrez-vous à dompter cet héritage et à devenir un Dieu Bénéfique... je"
" ne peux dire ce qui va arriver."

#: balth_finsol.tra:1014
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I just ask you to consider how Bhaal's taint has affected your life to this "
#| "point.  Do you really wish to have all of it?  What type of person actually "
#| "wishes to become a god?  Sarevok?  Irenicus?  Melissan?  Even if your "
#| "intentions are good, what of an eternity being chained to such power?"
msgid ""
"I just ask you to consider how Bhaal's taint has affected your life to this "
"point. Do you really wish to have all of it? What type of person actually "
"wishes to become a god? Sarevok? Irenicus? Melissan? Even if your intentions"
" are good, what of an eternity being chained to such power?"
msgstr ""
"Je vous demande juste de considérer de quelle façon la marque de Bhaal a "
"affecté votre vie jusqu'à aujourd'hui. Souhaitez-vous vraiment avoir tout ça"
" ? Quel genre de personnes veulent devenir des Dieux ? Sarevok ? Irenicus ? "
"Mélissane ? Même si vos intentions sont bonnes, qu'en est-il d'une éternité "
"liée par un tel pouvoir ?"

#: balth_finsol.tra:1015
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The choice is your own.  You know yourself better than I.  I simply ask that"
#| " you consider the life you might have led, the mortal life, had the taint "
#| "never visited itself upon you back at Candlekeep.  I look forward to my own."
msgid ""
"The choice is your own. You know yourself better than I. I simply ask that "
"you consider the life you might have led, the mortal life, had the taint "
"never visited itself upon you back at Candlekeep. I look forward to my own."
msgstr ""
"Le choix vous appartient. Vous vous connaissez mieux que moi. Je vous "
"demande simplement de considérer le vie que vous avez menée, la vie mortelle"
" à Châteausuif avant que cet héritage n'arrive dans votre vie."

#: balth_finsol.tra:1016
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And so it is done.  I believe you have made the right choice.  I look "
#| "forward to meeting you again on FaerÃ»n, <CHARNAME>...as a mortal and a true"
#| " <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>."
msgid ""
"And so it is done. I believe you have made the right choice. I look forward "
"to meeting you again on Faerun, <CHARNAME>...as a mortal and a true "
"<PRO_BROTHERSISTER>."
msgstr ""
"Et ainsi c'est fait. Je crois que vous avez fait le bon choix. J'espère vous"
" rencontrer à nouveau à Féerune, <CHARNAME>... en tant que mortel et "
"véritable frère."

#: balth_finsol.tra:1017
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And so you take the road less traveled, <CHARNAME>.  I cannot say I envy "
#| "you.  I hope the power brings you what you expect and desire, my friend.  "
#| "When I look up at the heavens and see the brightest star in the sky, I shall"
#| " think of you and offer a prayer."
msgid ""
"And so you take the road less traveled, <CHARNAME>. I cannot say I envy you."
" I hope the power brings you what you expect and desire, my friend. When I "
"look up at the heavens and see the brightest star in the sky, I shall think "
"of you and offer a prayer."
msgstr ""
"Et ainsi vous prenez le chemin que peu ont suivi, <CHARNAME>. Je ne peux pas"
" dire que je vous envie. J'espère que le pouvoir vous apportera ce que vous "
"désirez, mon ami. Quand je regarderai les cieux et que je verrai l'étoile la"
" plus brillante dans le ciel, je penserai à vous et vous adresserai une "
"prière."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:72
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I require satisfaction before the Child of Bhaal makes any sort of decision,"
#| " creature.  Both my brother and this... Melissan, lie dead.  Your hunt has "
#| "been delightfully successful, <CHARNAME>."
msgid ""
"I require satisfaction before the Child of Bhaal makes any sort of decision,"
" creature. Both my brother and this... Melissan, lie dead. Your hunt has "
"been delightfully successful, <CHARNAME>."
msgstr ""
"Je suis satisfaite que l'Enfant de Bhaal ait fait ce choix, créature. Aussi "
"bien mon frère que cette... Mélissane, sont morts. Ta chasse a été "
"délicieusement victorieuse, <CHARNAME>."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:73
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But do not forget our deal.  I am impatient for the piece of your soul you "
#| "promised me.  I have enjoyed our dance Child of Bhaal, but I tire of this "
#| "place.  Give me what I want so I may leave... we need not meet each other "
