msgid ""
"But do not forget our deal. I am impatient for the piece of your soul you "
"promised me. I have enjoyed our dance Child of Bhaal, but I tire of this "
"place. Give me what I want so I may leave... we need not meet each other "
"again, unless you wish it."
msgstr ""
"Mais n'oublie pas notre marché. Je suis impatiente d'avoir le fragment d'âme"
" que tu m'as promis. J'ai aimé notre danse, Enfant de Bhaal, mais je suis "
"fatiguée de cet endroit. Donne-moi ce que je veux, que je puisse m'en "
"aller... nous n'avons plus à nous revoir, à moins que tu ne le veuilles."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:74
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It was a pleasure to have you fight by my side, Bodhi.  You have earned this"
#| " reward."
msgid ""
"It was a pleasure to have you fight by my side, Bodhi. You have earned this "
"reward."
msgstr ""
"C'était un plaisir de t'avoir à mes côtés pour combattre, Bodhi. Tu as "
"mérité cette récompense."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:75
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You shall have nothing.  Your use to me is at an end.  I shall enjoy sending"
#| " you screaming back into the abyss."
msgid ""
"You shall have nothing. Your use to me is at an end. I shall enjoy sending "
"you screaming back into the abyss."
msgstr ""
"Tu n'auras rien. Je t'ai utilisée pour en arriver là. Je vais me réjouir à "
"l'idée de t'envoyer hurler à nouveau dans les Abysses."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:76
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Hmmm, I could kill you... no, I have better things to do.  Take these scraps"
#| " of my essence and depart."
msgid ""
"Hmmm, I could kill you... no, I have better things to do. Take these scraps "
"of my essence and depart."
msgstr ""
"Hmmm, je pourrais te tuer... non, j'ai mieux à faire. Prends ces débris "
"d'âme et vas-t'en."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:77
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No Bodhi, I think I will keep all of my soul.  You will fall back into the "
#| "abyss.  Give Bhaal my regards."
msgid ""
"No Bodhi, I think I will keep all of my soul. You will fall back into the "
"abyss. Give Bhaal my regards."
msgstr ""
"Non Bodhi, je pense que je vais garder toute mon âme. Tu vas retourner dans "
"les Abysses. Salue Bhaal de ma part."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:78
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Fool!  You think to betray me, Child of Bhaal?  I refuse to return to the "
#| "abyss.  I shall rip every shred of that soul from your body!  Let the dance "
#| "end here!"
msgid ""
"Fool! You think to betray me, Child of Bhaal? I refuse to return to the "
"abyss. I shall rip every shred of that soul from your body! Let the dance "
"end here!"
msgstr ""
"Idiot ! Tu penses me trahir, Enfant de Bhaal ? Je refuse de retourner dans "
"les Abysses ! Je vais arracher chaque morceau d'âme de ton corps ! Que cette"
" danse se termine ici même !"

#: bodhi_solar.tra:79
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This is my realm, Bodhi.  I control everything here.  It is time for you to "
#| "join your brother."
msgid ""
"This is my realm, Bodhi. I control everything here. It is time for you to "
"join your brother."
msgstr ""
"C'est mon Royaume, Bodhi. Je contrôle tout ici. Il est temps pour toi de "
"rejoindre ton frère."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:80
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Enough talk!  The dance has come to an end, Bodhi, and so has your part in "
#| "it."
msgid ""
"Enough talk! The dance has come to an end, Bodhi, and so has your part in "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Assez parlé ! La danse touche à sa fin, Bodhi, et il en va de même pour ta "
"participation."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:81
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Die!  Witness my power, insect!"
msgid "Die! Witness my power, insect!"
msgstr "Meurs ! Contemples ma puissance, insecte !"

#: bodhi_solar.tra:82
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh Bodhi, you should have begged.  I would have liked to see that.  Too late"
#| " now."
msgid ""
"Oh Bodhi, you should have begged. I would have liked to see that. Too late "
"now."
msgstr ""
"Oh Bodhi, tu aurais dû me supplier. J'aurais aimé voir ça. Il est trop tard "
"maintenant."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:83
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So you have betrayed me, <CHARNAME>.  It would seem that working together "
#| "was never our true calling."
msgid ""
"So you have betrayed me, <CHARNAME>. It would seem that working together was"
" never our true calling."
msgstr ""
"Ainsi tu m'as trahie, <CHARNAME>. On dirait que travailler ensemble n'a "
"jamais été notre vocation."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:84
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ahhhhh, such feeling.  I feel the life flow through me!  Such a gift you "
#| "carry Child of Bhaal...  such power...  such strength.  Oh this is simply "
#| "divine!"
msgid ""
"Ahhhhh, such feeling. I feel the life flow through me! Such a gift you carry"
" Child of Bhaal... such power... such strength. Oh this is simply divine!"
msgstr ""
"Ahhhhh, un tel sentiment. Je sens la vie au travers de moi ! Tu portes un "
"tel don, Enfant de Bhaal...  un tel pouvoir... une telle force. Oh c'est "
"tout simplement divin !"

#: bodhi_solar.tra:85
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Such an ungrateful <PRO_MANWOMAN> you are.  Still, I have life once more, "
#| "and I intend to enjoy it.  Perhaps the wizards of Spellhold still wish to "
#| "play?"
msgid ""
"Such an ungrateful <PRO_MANWOMAN> you are. Still, I have life once more, and"
" I intend to enjoy it. Perhaps the wizards of Spellhold still wish to play?"
msgstr ""
"Quelle personne ingrate tu fais. Pourtant, je vis à nouveau, et j'espère en "
"profiter. Peut-être que les mages de Spellhold ont envie de jouer ?"

#: bodhi_solar.tra:86
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Well, Child of Bhaal, it would seem that our time together is at an end.  I "
#| "shall enjoy carrying this piece of you with me.  Perhaps we shall meet "
#| "again, you and I..."
msgid ""
"Well, Child of Bhaal, it would seem that our time together is at an end. I "
"shall enjoy carrying this piece of you with me. Perhaps we shall meet again,"
" you and I..."
msgstr ""
"Bien, Enfant de Bhaal, il semble que notre coopération touche à sa fin. Je "
"vais être heureuse de transporter cette partie de toi avec moi. Peut-être "
"nous reverrons-nous à nouveau, juste toi et moi..."

#: bodhi_solar.tra:586
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "While it fills me with distaste that you would even bring such a creature of"
#| " evil before me, god-child, you must remember that in this place an oath is "
#| "worth more than the words with which it is spoken.  You are no god yet... "
#| "and while I would rather destroy this undead thing, it now falls on me to "
#| "enforce the promise you have made."
msgid ""
"While it fills me with distaste that you would even bring such a creature of"
" evil before me, god-child, you must remember that in this place an oath is "
"worth more than the words with which it is spoken. You are no god yet... and"
" while I would rather destroy this undead thing, it now falls on me to "
"enforce the promise you have made."
msgstr ""
"Bien que cela me remplisse de répugnance que tu emmènes une telle créature "
"maléfique devant moi, enfant divin, tu dois te souvenir qu'en ce lieu un "
"serment a plus de valeur que les mots dont il est fait. Tu n'es pas encore "
"un Dieu... et bien que je préférerais détruire cette abomination morte-"
"vivante, il m'appartient maintenant de tenir la promesse que tu as faite."

#: description.tra:1
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Imoen Has Survived\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Imoen managed to survive Melissan's attempt to force her into berserk Slayer form.  It seems that in doing so, Imoen has had her own progress in the taint advanced considerably.  She now not only can turn into the same Slayer form that I began to back in Spellhold... but has also gained the ability to go ethereal for brief periods of time.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Ethereal\n"
#| "-------------\n"
#| "Imoen is now able to enter the Ethereal Plane for brief periods of time.  The ability is useable once every minute, and its use prevents her from assuming the Slayer form for a minute, as well.  Imoen can remain fully ethereal and intangible to forces on this plane for a full round... during which she is invisible and completely immune to harm.  During that round, she also cannot cast spells or use abilities.\n"
#| "For another two rounds afterwards, Imoen can remain 'half-phased'...she is partially ethereal and partially in this plane.  She is still invisible, but takes half damage from all sources.  In this state, there is a small chance (10%) that she will miscast a spell.  For all three rounds, she is able to see any invisible targets."
msgid ""
"Ethereal\n"
"\n"
"Imoen is now able to enter the Ethereal Plane for brief periods of time. The ability is useable once every minute, and its use prevents her from assuming the Slayer form for a minute, as well. Imoen can remain fully ethereal and intangible to forces on this plane for a full round... during which she is invisible and completely immune to harm. During that round, she also cannot cast spells or use abilities.\n"
"\n"
"For another two rounds afterwards, Imoen remains 'half-phased'...she is partially ethereal and partially in this plane. She is still invisible, but takes half damage from all sources. In this state, there is a small chance (10%) that she will miscast a spell. For all three rounds, she is able to see any invisible targets."
msgstr ""
"Imoen a survécu\n"
"\n"
"Imoen a réussi à survivre à la tentative de Mélissane de la condamner à la forme d'Ecorcheuse. Il semble que ce faisant, Imoen a vu la maîtrise de son essence progresser de façon considérable. Elle peut désormais non seulement prendre la même forme d'Ecorcheur que celle que j'avais revêtu à Spellhold... mais a aussi acquis la capacité de devenir éthérée pour de brèves périodes.\n"
"\n"
"Ethérée\n"
"-------------\n"
"Imoen peut à présent entrer dans le plan éthéré pour de brèves périodes. Cette capacité est utilisable une fois par minute, et son utilisation l'empêche de prendre la forme d'Ecorcheuse pendant une minute également. Imoen peut rester complètement éthérée et intangible sur ce plan pour un round complet... au cours duquel elle est invisible et complètement immunisée aux dégâts. Pendant ce round, elle est également dans l'impossibilité de jeter des sorts ou d'utiliser d'autres capacités.\n"
"Pour les deux rounds suivants, Imoen peut rester en 'demi-phase'... partiellement éthérée et partiellement dans ce plan. Elle est toujours invisible mais ne reçoit que la moitié des dégâts de n'importe quelle source. Dans cet état, il y a une faible chance (10%) qu'elle puisse rater un sort. Pour la totalité des trois rounds, elle est capable de voir les cibles invisibles."

#: description.tra:6
msgid ""
"End Slayer Change\n"
"\n"
"This ability allows Imoen to cancel her transformation and return to her usual form."
msgstr ""

