#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Actually Bodhi, I have changed my mind.  I enjoy watching you die too much, "
#| "to pass up an opportunity to see it again."
msgid ""
"Actually Bodhi, I have changed my mind. I enjoy watching you die too much, "
"to pass up an opportunity to see it again."
msgstr ""
"Finalement Bodhi, j'ai changé d'avis. J'aime tellement te voir mourir, je ne"
" vais pas laisser passer une occasion de voir ça à nouveau."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:69
msgid "Bodhi, when this is over, I swear that you will be fittingly rewarded."
msgstr ""
"Bodhi, quand tout ceci sera fini, je te jure que tu seras grandement "
"récompensée."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:70
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Pray that you hold to your word, failure to do so would be... unpleasant for"
#| " you.  Now to finalize matters..."
msgid ""
"Pray that you hold to your word, failure to do so would be... unpleasant for"
" you. Now to finalize matters..."
msgstr ""
"Tiens ta parole, ne pas le faire aurait des conséquences... très "
"déplaisantes pour toi. Maintenant pour conclure les choses..."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:71
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "No, <CHARNAME>.  Sadly, I do not think we are destined to work together "
#| "again.  Despite the attractiveness of what you offer, your words ring more "
#| "hollow than my brother's.  Far better to rip your soul from your living "
#| "breast than beg for it at your side."
msgid ""
"No, <CHARNAME>. Sadly, I do not think we are destined to work together "
"again. Despite the attractiveness of what you offer, your words ring more "
"hollow than my brother's. Far better to rip your soul from your living "
"breast than beg for it at your side."
msgstr ""
"Non, <CHARNAME>. Malheureusement, je ne pense pas que nous soyons destinés à"
" travailler ensembles. En dépit de l'attrait de ce que tu m'offres, tes mots"
" ont moins de consistance que ceux de mon frère. Je préfère arracher ton âme"
" de ton corps encore chaud plutôt que de la mendier à tes pieds."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:87
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Now, now, <CHARNAME>...there is no need to look at me so.  A tiny piece of "
#| "your soul would give me all I require and more.  Decide quickly, for I doubt"
#| " my dear brother will be content with merely withering me with his own "
#| "delightfully evil glare."
msgid ""
"Now, now, <CHARNAME>...there is no need to look at me so. A tiny piece of "
"your soul would give me all I require and more. Decide quickly, for I doubt "
"my dear brother will be content with merely withering me with his own "
"delightfully evil glare."
msgstr ""
"<CHARNAME>... il n'y a pas de raison de me regarder ainsi. Une petite partie"
" de ton âme me donnera tout ce qu'il me fait et bien plus encore. Décide-"
"toi."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:88
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Why you assumed I would even be interested in your allegiance, Bodhi, I have"
#| " no idea.  I shall be pleased to know that you both die again just as you "
#| "lived: without a single redeeming or worthwhile quality."
msgid ""
"Why you assumed I would even be interested in your allegiance, Bodhi, I have"
" no idea. I shall be pleased to know that you both die again just as you "
"lived: without a single redeeming or worthwhile quality."
msgstr ""
"Pourquoi tu crois que je puisse être intéressé par ton allégeance, Bodhi, je"
" n'en ai aucune idée. Je serais heureux lorsque vous mourrez tout deux de "
"nouveau comme vous avez vécu : sans rédemption ni valeur."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:452
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do not overestimate your usefulness to me, 'dear' sister... nor the extent "
#| "of my non-existent affection.  Or do you truly think I had forgotten your "
#| "whispered urgings which had led me down the path of my exile?"
msgid ""
"Do not overestimate your usefulness to me, 'dear' sister... nor the extent "
"of my non-existent affection. Or do you truly think I had forgotten your "
"whispered urgings which had led me down the path of my exile?"
msgstr ""
"Ne surestime pas ton utilité pour moi, 'chère' soeur... ni l'étendue de mon "
"manque d'affection pour toi. Penses-tu vraiment que j'ai oublié tes murmures"
" à mon oreille qui m'ont conduit à mon exil ?"

#: iren_bodhi.tra:453
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Enough, sister.  We do as Melissan bids, with her servants at our side.  "
#| "Take delight, if you will, at the revenge we shall now taste.  Let us see, "
#| "<CHARNAME>, if I can rip that soul out of you once more.  I would so delight"
#| " in stealing your proud destiny a second time."
msgid ""
"Enough, sister. We do as Melissan bids, with her servants at our side. Take "
"delight, if you will, at the revenge we shall now taste. Let us see, "
"<CHARNAME>, if I can rip that soul out of you once more. I would so delight "
"in stealing your proud destiny a second time."
msgstr ""
"Assez, soeur. Faisons ce que demande Mélissane, avec ses serviteurs à nos "
"côtés. Prends du plaisir, si tu le veux, à la revanche à laquelle nous "
"allons goûter. Voyons, <CHARNAME>, si je peux t'arracher ton âme une "
"nouvelle fois. Je serais heureux de te voler à nouveau ta fierté."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:454
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You over-step your bounds, as always.  I did not call you here to rejoice in"
#| " your venom, Bodhi.  Do you not notice where we are?  Whom we face?"
msgid ""
"You over-step your bounds, as always. I did not call you here to rejoice in "
"your venom, Bodhi. Do you not notice where we are? Whom we face?"
msgstr ""
"Tu surestimes ton utilité, comme toujours. Je ne t'ai pas fait venir pour me"
" réjouir de ton venin, Bodhi. Remarques-tu où nous sommes ? A qui nous "
"faisons face ?"

#: iren_bodhi.tra:455
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You think to betray me, Bodhi?  Foolish girl.  Melissan is the one who holds"
#| " power here, and you hope to find succor at the feet of this fool "
#| "<PRO_GIRLBOY>?  Stand by me or die with <PRO_HIMHER>!"
msgid ""
"You think to betray me, Bodhi? Foolish girl. Melissan is the one who holds "
"power here, and you hope to find succor at the feet of this fool "
"<PRO_GIRLBOY>? Stand by me or die with <PRO_HIMHER>!"
msgstr ""
"Tu songes à me trahir, Bodhi ? Idiote. Mélissane est celle qui a la toute "
"puissance ici, et tu penses trouver le succès aux pieds de cet imbécile ? "
"Viens avec moi ou meurs avec lui !"

#: iren_bodhi.tra:456
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So my ungrateful sister, you finally stand by my side.  I shall deal with "
#| "your treachery afterwards.  As for you,  <CHARNAME>, Mellisan has granted me"
#| " the power to rip the divinity from your body.  The first thing I shall feel"
#| " in an eon shall be pleasure as I watch your corpse turn to dust."
msgid ""
"So my ungrateful sister, you finally stand by my side. I shall deal with "
"your treachery afterwards. As for you, <CHARNAME>, Melissan has granted me "
"the power to rip the divinity from your body. The first thing I shall feel "
"in an eon shall be pleasure as I watch your corpse turn to dust."
msgstr ""
"Donc, ma soeur ingrate, tu te tiens finalement à mes côtés. Je me chargerai "
"de ta trahison plus tard. Te concernant, <CHARNAME>, Mélissane m'a donné le "
"pouvoir de retirer la divinité de ton corps. Des années plus tard je me "
"rappellerai encore du plaisir ressenti en contemplant ton corps réduit en "
"poussière."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:457
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I see.  So you leave me, sister, just as *she* left me."
msgid "I see. So you leave me, sister, just as *she* left me."
msgstr ""
"Je vois. Donc tu m'abandonnes, soeur, tout comme *elle* m'a abandonné."

#: iren_bodhi.tra:458
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It is no matter.  Melissan has given me power enough, and her own servants "
#| "shall teach you the error of your ways.  I shall strip the divinity from "
#| "<CHARNAME>'s soul and you, *dear* sister, shall be nothing but dust beside "
#| "<PRO_HIMHER>."
msgid ""
"It is no matter. Melissan has given me power enough, and her own servants "
"shall teach you the error of your ways. I shall strip the divinity from "
"<CHARNAME>'s soul and you, *dear* sister, shall be nothing but dust beside "
"<PRO_HIMHER>."
msgstr ""
"Ca n'a aucune importance. Mélissane m'a donné suffisamment de puissance, et "
"ses propres serviteurs t'apprendront les erreurs de tes choix. Je vais "
"détruire la divinité de <CHARNAME> et toi, *chère* soeur, ne sera rien "
"d'autre qu'un tas de poussière à ses côtés."

#: iren_sarev.tra:277
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This is the Irenicus I have been told of?  I was expecting more intensity "
#| "and power from one who hounded <CHARNAME> so, and not "
#| "simply...*another*...wizard."
msgid ""
"This is the Irenicus I have been told of? I was expecting more intensity and"
" power from one who hounded <CHARNAME> so, and not "
"simply...*another*...wizard."
msgstr ""
"C'est ça le fameux Irenicus dont ont m'a parlé ? Je m'attendais à plus "
"d'intensité et de puissance de la part de quelqu'un qui avait pourchassé "
"<CHARNAME> de cette façon, et pas simplement un magicien de plus."

#: iren_sarev.tra:278
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yet I certainly would not have allowed <CHARNAME> to escape from me, had "
#| "<PRO_HESHE> been within my power not once but twice, even.  But, then, I "
#| "imagine you were too busy taking control of insane asylums and making "
#| "thieves out of vampires for absolutely no reason."
msgid ""
"Yet I certainly would not have allowed <CHARNAME> to escape from me, had "
"<PRO_HESHE> been within my power not once but twice, even. But, then, I "
"imagine you were too busy taking control of insane asylums and making "
"thieves out of vampires for absolutely no reason."
msgstr ""
"Pourtant, je n'aurais certainement pas laissé <CHARNAME> m'échapper, deux "
"fois qui plus est. Mais bon, j'imagine que tu étais plus occupé à prendre le"
" contrôle d'asiles d'aliénés et à faire s'affronter des voleurs et des "
"vampires sans raison."

#: iren_sarev.tra:440
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So, <CHARNAME>...it is now just you and I, once again.  At odds in the "
#| "bowels of Hell and preparing to do combat.  How very fitting."
msgid ""
"So, <CHARNAME>...it is now just you and I, once again. At odds in the bowels"
" of Hell and preparing to do combat. How very fitting."
msgstr ""
"Ainsi, <CHARNAME>... ce n'est maintenant qu'entre toi et moi, une fois de "
"plus. Aux frontières de l'Enfer, prêts à nous battre. Tout à fait adapté."

#: iren_sarev.tra:441
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This fight is mine, Irenicus.  While you stewed in Hell, my power has "
#| "multiplied."
msgid ""
"This fight is mine, Irenicus. While you stewed in Hell, my power has "
"multiplied."
msgstr ""
"Ce combat est mien, Irenicus. Pendant que tu pourrissais en Enfer, mon "
"pouvoir s'est décuplé."

#: iren_sarev.tra:442
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You actually think you'll stop me?  It appears your delusions have survived "
#| "the many beatings at my hand."
msgid ""
"You actually think you'll stop me? It appears your delusions have survived "
"the many beatings at my hand."
msgstr ""
"Tu penses vraiment pouvoir me stopper ? Il semble que tes délires aient "
"survécu aux nombreux coups que tu as reçu de ma main."

#: iren_sarev.tra:443
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So you're actually willing to serve as Melissan's little lackey?  I would "
#| "expect more from the great elven magician.  Ellesime would be sad to see you"
#| " reduced to this."
msgid ""
"So you're actually willing to serve as Melissan's little lackey? I would "
"expect more from the great elven magician. Ellesime would be sad to see you "
"reduced to this."
msgstr ""
"Alors tu es vraiment désireux de servir comme le petit laquais de Mélissane "
"? J'espérais mieux de la part du grand mage elfe. Ellesime serait triste de "
"te voir réduit à ça."

#: iren_sarev.tra:444
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Don't you ever tire of that bravado?  Haven't you received enough spankings "
#| "upon my knee?"
msgid ""
"Don't you ever tire of that bravado? Haven't you received enough spankings "
"upon my knee?"
msgstr ""
"N'es-tu jamais fatigué de ta bravade ? N'as-tu pas reçu suffisamment de "
"coups ?"

#: iren_sarev.tra:445
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You won't stop me, Irenicus.  Nobody can.  My destiny is at hand."
msgid "You won't stop me, Irenicus. Nobody can. My destiny is at hand."
msgstr ""
"Tu ne m'arrêteras pas, Irenicus. Personne ne le peut. Ma destinée est à "
"portée de main."

#: iren_sarev.tra:446
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It appears you have been the beneficiary of low expectations, but even I "
#| "have learned from my mistakes.  Here, I have nothing to lose, not even my "
#| "life.  Thanks to Melissan, I still have time to snuff out your divine "
#| "ascencion personally. We will be even!"
msgid ""
"It appears you have been the beneficiary of low expectations, but even I "
"have learned from my mistakes. Here, I have nothing to lose, not even my "
"life. Thanks to Melissan, I still have time to snuff out your divine "
"ascencion personally. We will be even!"
msgstr ""
"Il apparaît que tu as eu beaucoup de chance, mais même moi j'ai tiré les "
"leçons de mes erreurs. Ici je n'ai rien à perdre, même pas ma vie. Grâce à "
"Mélissane, j'ai l'occasion de stopper ton ascension divine de mes propres "
"mains. Nous serons à égalité !"

#: iren_sarev.tra:447
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You may have gained some crude and rudimentary control over your abilities "
#| "in the interim, but even I have learned a thing or two... delusions or no.  "
#| "And Melissan has given me the opportunity to personally see an end to your "
#| "ascension... consider it a favor returned."
msgid ""
"You may have gained some crude and rudimentary control over your abilities "
"in the interim, but even I have learned a thing or two... delusions or no. "
"And Melissan has given me the opportunity to personally see an end to your "
"ascension... consider it a favor returned."
msgstr ""
"Tu as peut-être un peu gagné en force et amélioré ton contrôle sur certaines"
" de tes capacités... mais moi aussi j'ai appris une ou deux choses, que tu "
"me croies ou non. Et Mélissane m'a donné l'opportunité d'assister à la fin "
"de ton ascension... considère que je vais te rendre ta \"faveur\"."

#: iren_sarev.tra:448
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Do not speak her name, dog.  Ellesime will understand the fullness of her "
#| "regret soon enough.  As for you... Melissan has given me the opportunity to "
#| "return an old favor.  One ascension for another... it rings with universal "
#| "justice."
msgid ""
"Do not speak her name, dog. Ellesime will understand the fullness of her "
"regret soon enough. As for you... Melissan has given me the opportunity to "
"return an old favor. One ascension for another... it rings with universal "
"justice."
msgstr ""
"Ne prononce pas son nom, chien ! Ellesime comprendra vite ses regrets, dans "
"peu de temps. Tout comme toi... Mélissane m'a donné l'opportunité de te "
"retourner une vieille faveur. Une ascension pour une autre... n'est-ce pas "
"que justice ?"

#: iren_sarev.tra:449
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "How very glib and typical.  How far the expectations of the universe must "
#| "have lowered to allow a gnat like you to even come this far.  It is "
#| "fortunate that I have an opportunity, then, to repay your termination of my "
#| "own ascension in kind."
msgid ""
"How very glib and typical. How far the expectations of the universe must "
"have lowered to allow a gnat like you to even come this far. It is fortunate"
" that I have an opportunity, then, to repay your termination of my own "
"ascension in kind."
msgstr ""
"C'est pitoyable. Comme les ambitions de l'Univers sont tombées bien bas pour"
" permettre à un microbe comme toi d'arriver aussi loin. C'est une grande "
"chance que j'aie l'occasion, à présent, de te faire payer pour avoir stoppé "
"ma propre ascension."

#: iren_sarev.tra:450
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ah, yes.  Familiar words.  Similar to the ones I spoke at the cusp of my own"
#| " ascension.  How I would enjoy to repay that favor in kind and show the "
#| "universe what an unworthy gnat you truly are."
msgid ""
"Ah, yes. Familiar words. Similar to the ones I spoke at the cusp of my own "
"ascension. How I would enjoy to repay that favor in kind and show the "
"universe what an unworthy gnat you truly are."
msgstr ""
"Ah, oui. Des mots familiers. Similaires à ceux que je proférais lors de ma "
"propre ascension. Comme je vais être heureux de te faire payer ça moi-même "
"et montrer à l'univers combien tu es insignifiant."

#: iren_sarev.tra:451
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But enough of this.  Though I would dearly love to let my sister rot in her "
#| "own Hell for eternity, it would not be a true and fitting re-union if I did "
#| "not use my new power to send her an invitation."
msgid ""
"But enough of this. Though I would dearly love to let my sister rot in her "
"own Hell for eternity, it would not be a true and fitting re-union if I did "
"not use my new power to send her an invitation."
msgstr ""
"Mais il suffit. Bien que j'aimerais laisser ma chère soeur brûler en Enfer "
"pour l'éternité, ce ne serait pas de véritables retrouvailles si je "
"n'utilisais mes pouvoirs pour lui envoyer une invitation."

#: iren_sarev.tra:459
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Better that than a laughable fool whose most promising idea to dominate the "
#| "Sword Coast was to 'poison' its supply of iron.  I discarded you as a "
#| "candidate long before <CHARNAME> soundly defeated you merely for fear of "
#| "losing all common sense merely by association with your pathetic soul."
msgid ""
"Better that than a laughable fool whose most promising idea to dominate the "
"Sword Coast was to 'poison' its supply of iron. I discarded you as a "
"candidate long before <CHARNAME> soundly defeated you merely for fear of "
"losing all common sense merely by association with your pathetic soul."
msgstr ""
"Mieux qu'un idiot ridicule dont la meilleure idée pour s'emparer de la Côte "
"des Epées était 'd'empoisonner' son approvisionnement en fer. Je t'ai "
"éliminé comme candidat bien avant que <CHARNAME> ne te batte, par crainte de"
" perdre tout sens commun en me mêlant à une âme aussi pathétique que la "
"tienne."

#: iren_sarev.tra:460
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Bark if you wish, mongrel.  Whatever dull fangs you might have possessed "
#| "have long since been pulled.  If a has-been wishes to ride <CHARNAME>'s "
#| "coat-tails it makes no difference to me... but you'll be disintegrated right"
#| " along with <PRO_HIMHER>."
msgid ""
"Bark if you wish, mongrel. Whatever dull fangs you might have possessed have"
" long since been pulled. If a has-been wishes to ride <CHARNAME>'s coat-"
"tails it makes no difference to me... but you'll be disintegrated right "
"along with <PRO_HIMHER>."
msgstr ""
"Fais le malin si tu veux, créature. Tes crocs t'ont été enlevés il y a bien "
"longtemps. Si un revenant veut suivre <CHARNAME> comme un petit chien, peu "
"m'importe... mais tu seras désintégré avec."

#: items-ee.tra:3001
msgid ""
"The blade of Sarevok, brother of <CHARNAME>, used in the battle they fought in faraway Baldur's Gate. <CHARNAME> prevailed, destroying Sarevok's plans and rescuing the Sword Coast from the brink of war. Now Sarevok has joined with <CHARNAME>'s cause and his blade has been restored to him. Sarevok describes the weapon as a Deathbringer blade and has restored some of the weapon's old power. Without his Bhaalspawn essence to channel through the sword, however, it cannot achieve the power it once had. Still, however, it is a formidable weapon...and one that Sarevok warns would become increasingly difficult to wield in the hands of one who was not a Deathbringer, if they could use it at all.\n"
"\n"
"STATISTICS:\n"
"\n"
"Combat abilities:\n"
"- Each hit drains one to five Hit Points from the target and transfers it to the wielder. This will not heal beyond the wielder's maximum.\n"
"\n"
"Equipped abilities:\n"
"- Magic Resistance: +10%\n"
"\n"
"THAC0: +4\n"
"Damage: 1d10+4 (slashing)\n"
"Speed Factor: 8\n"
"Proficiency Type: Two-handed Sword\n"
"Type: Two-handed\n"
"\n"
"Requires:\n"
"14 Strength\n"
"18 Constitution\n"
"\n"
"Weight: 10"
msgstr ""
"Il s'agit de l'arme de Sarevok, frère de <CHARNAME>, qui fut utilisée dans la bataille de la Porte de Baldur. <CHARNAME> a gagné, ruinant ainsi les plans de Sarevok, et sauvant la Côte des Epées de la guerre. Maintenant, Sarevok s'est joint à la cause de <CHARNAME> et son épée lui a été rendue. Sarevok décrit cette arme comme une Lame Fatale et a restauré une partie des anciens pouvoirs de cet objet. Cependant, sans son essence d'Enfant de Bhaal pour nourrir l'épée, il n'a pu lui rendre la totalité du pouvoir qu'elle possédait autrefois. Quoiqu'il en soit, elle reste une arme formidable... et Sarevok prévient qu'elle deviendrait très difficile à utiliser dans les mains de quelqu'un qui ne fût pas un Porteur de Mort, voire impossible à utiliser.\n"
"\n"
"PARAMETRES :\n"
"\n"
"Capacités de combat : chaque coup porté draine de 1 à 5 points de vie de la cible et les transfère au porteur (qui ne peut pas dépasser son maximum).\n"
"\n"
"La lame procure également +10% de Résistance à la Magie lorsqu'elle est équipée.\n"
"\n"
"Dégâts : 1D10 +4\n"
"TAC0 : +4\n"
"Type de dégâts : tranchant\n"
"Poids : 10\n"
"Facteur de Vitesse : 8\n"
"Type de compétence : Epée à 2 mains\n"
"Type :  à 2 mains\n"
"Prérequis : 14 en Force, 18 en Constitution\n"
"Inutilisable par :\n"
"Clerc\n"
"Mage\n"
"Paladin\n"
"Rôdeur\n"
"Druide\n"
"Personnages d'alignement Non Chaotiques"

#: items-ee.tra:3003
