msgid ""
"Oh no? Perhaps you do not understand. This... this place, here, is the "
"Source. This is where the essence of all of Bhaal's children returns when "
"they die, hidden away. Did you never wonder, dear Balthazar, what killing "
"all the other spawn of Bhaal was *for*?"
msgstr ""
"Oh non ? Peut-être que tu ne comprends pas. Ce... ce lieu, ici, est la "
"Source. C'est ici que les essences de tous les Enfants de Bhaal retournant à"
" leur mort, cachée du monde. Ne t'es-tu jamais demandé, cher Balthazar, à "
"quoi servait l'extermination des autres Enfants de Bhaal ?"

#: mel_balth.tra:615
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And well you should not have, though you aided me regardless.  Bhaal may, "
#| "indeed, be... somewhere.  But not here.  Here I have locked these essences "
#| "away and drank heartily of their power.  The Source, the Throne, all are "
#| "mine... and god-hood is but one simple step away."
msgid ""
"And well you should not have, though you aided me regardless. Bhaal may, "
"indeed, be... somewhere. But not here. Here I have locked these essences "
"away and drank heartily of their power. The Source, the Throne, all are "
"mine... and god-hood is but one simple step away."
msgstr ""
"Et tu m'as aveuglement aidée. Bhaal est peut-être quelque part... mais pas "
"ici. J'ai emprisonné les âmes ici et bu leur puissance. La Source, le Trône,"
" tout ceci est à moi... et la Déité n'est qu'une simple étape vers la suite."

#: mel_balth.tra:1002
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<CHARNAME> does not stand alone, Melissan.  It is time that this is ended."
msgid ""
"<CHARNAME> does not stand alone, Melissan. It is time that this is ended."
msgstr ""
"<CHARNAME> n'est pas seul, Mélissane. C'est ici que tout va se terminer."

#: mel_balth.tra:1003
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I see well enough now, priestess.  Speak clever wit if you wish, you cannot "
#| "hope to defeat us."
msgid ""
"I see well enough now, priestess. Speak clever wit if you wish, you cannot "
"hope to defeat us."
msgstr ""
"Je vois clair à présent, prêtresse. Parles si tu veux, tu ne peux espérer "
"nous vaincre."

#: mel_balth.tra:1004
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "To return the essence to our father.  And great bloodshed in his name to "
#| "call him forth.  And I never believed it."
msgid ""
"To return the essence to our father. And great bloodshed in his name to call"
" him forth. And I never believed it."
msgstr ""
"Pour réunir l'essence de notre père. Et verser beaucoup de sang en son nom "
"pour le rappeler. Et je n'y ai jamais cru."

#: mel_banter.tra:630
#, fuzzy
