"That's okay. If Sarevok can turn up like a bad penny, then you're allowed "
"to, as well."
msgstr ""
"Cela m'est égal. Si Sarevok peut être apprivoisé, alors toi aussi je pense."

#: mel_iren_imoen.tra:437
#, fuzzy
