#: the_five.tra:28
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "So you die again, as well.  It's all good."
msgid "So you die again, as well. It's all good."
msgstr "Et tu mourras une nouvelle fois. Pas de problème."

#: the_five.tra:29
msgid "You're a fool, Sarevok, if you think you'll make any difference."
msgstr ""
"Tu es un idiot Sarevok si tu penses que tu vas faire une quelconque "
"différence."

#: the_five.tra:30
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You're willing to become Melissan's servant, now?  I'm disappointed."
