msgid ""
"Serve you? You made me that offer once, as I recall. I strung up your "
"messenger atop the spires of my tower and allowed the crows to feed upon his"
" innards. I desired to rule, not to serve. And I will not serve you, wench. "
"My answer is no."
msgstr ""
"Te servir ? Tu m'as déjà fait cette proposition, si je me rappelle bien. "
"J'ai planté ton messager sur le sommet de ma tour et ai laissé les corbeaux "
"se régaler de ses chairs. Je désire commander, pas servir. Et je ne te "
"servirai pas, femme. Ma réponse est non."

#: the_five.tra:266
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I tire of <CHARNAME> and <PRO_HISHER> foolish morals.  I tire of tagging "
#| "along as a servant to the one who halted my own plans long before yours came"
#| " to fruition, priestess.  Aye... I will be your general."
msgid ""
"I tire of <CHARNAME> and <PRO_HISHER> foolish morals. I tire of tagging "
"along as a servant to the one who halted my own plans long before yours came"
" to fruition, priestess. Aye... I will be your general."
msgstr ""
"Je suis fatigué de <CHARNAME> et de sa stupide morale. Je suis fatigué de "
"suivre comme un serviteur la personne qui a stoppé mes plans bien avant que "
"les tiens ne portent leurs fruits, prêtresse. D'accord... je serai ton "
"général."

#: the_five.tra:267
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "No, Sarevok!  You traitorous bastard!"
msgid "No, Sarevok! You traitorous bastard!"
msgstr "Non, Sarevok ! Saleté de traître !"

#: the_five.tra:268
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "That is a mistake, Sarevok.  You'll just die along with her this way."
msgid "That is a mistake, Sarevok. You'll just die along with her this way."
msgstr "C'est une erreur, Sarevok. Tu vas juste mourir à ses côtés."

#: the_five.tra:269
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I expected as much.  So I get to kill you again, as well.  It's all good."
msgid ""
"I expected as much. So I get to kill you again, as well. It's all good."
msgstr ""
"Je m'y attendais. Donc je vais devoir te tuer à nouveau. Cela me convient."

#: the_five.tra:270
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Become the demon I once was?  I am no longer that man, nor do I wish to be."
#| "  If <CHARNAME> has shown me anything, it is that I am better off untouched "
#| "by the madness that once swallowed me whole.  Wallow in your delusion if you"
#| " will, woman... I remember it well.  And I will not join you in it."
msgid ""
"Become the demon I once was? I am no longer that man, nor do I wish to be. "
"If <CHARNAME> has shown me anything, it is that I am better off untouched by"
" the madness that once swallowed me whole. Wallow in your delusion if you "
"will, woman... I remember it well. And I will not join you in it."
msgstr ""
"Redevenir le démon que j'étais ? Je ne suis plus cet homme, et je ne veux "
"plus l'être. Si <CHARNAME> m'a bien montré quelque chose, c'est que je me "
"porte mieux sans cette folie qui avait touché mon esprit. Berces-toi "
"d'illusions si tu le souhaites, femme... moi aussi j'ai connu ça. Et je ne "
"t'accompagnerai pas là-dedans."

#: the_five.tra:271
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "My nature has not changed, <CHARNAME>.  Did you truly expect otherwise?  "
#| "Better to fight for Melissan than sit in your shadow and watch you take what"
#| " was once mine."
msgid ""
"My nature has not changed, <CHARNAME>. Did you truly expect otherwise? "
"Better to fight for Melissan than sit in your shadow and watch you take what"
" was once mine."
msgstr ""
"Ma nature n'a pas changé, <CHARNAME>. Espérais-tu vraiment autre chose ? Je "
"préfère me battre pour Mélissane plutôt que de rester dans ton ombre et te "
"voir prendre ce qui aurait dû me revenir."

#: the_five.tra:272
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps.  But I will not sit in your shadow and simply watch you take what "
#| "was once mine.  You do not deserve power, <CHARNAME>.  Even if it means "
#| "fighting for Melissan, I will do what I must."
msgid ""
"Perhaps. But I will not sit in your shadow and simply watch you take what "
"was once mine. You do not deserve power, <CHARNAME>. Even if it means "
"fighting for Melissan, I will do what I must."
msgstr ""
"Peut-être. Mais je ne vais pas rester dans ton ombre et te regarder prendre "
"ce qui me revenait. Tu ne mérites pas ce pouvoir, <CHARNAME>. Je ferai ce "
"que je dois faire, même si cela signifie me battre pour Mélissane."

#: the_five.tra:273
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "A typical boast.  And perhaps you will even win, but I will not sit idly by "
#| "as you take what was once mine.  You don't deserve power, <CHARNAME>, and "
#| "even if it means fighting for Melissan I will do what I must."
msgid ""
"A typical boast. And perhaps you will even win, but I will not sit idly by "
"as you take what was once mine. You don't deserve power, <CHARNAME>, and "
"even if it means fighting for Melissan I will do what I must."
msgstr ""
"Une réponse typique. Et tu peux même être vainqueur, mais je ne m'assoirai "
"pas tranquillement en te regardant prendre ce qui me revenait. Tu ne mérites"
" pas ce pouvoir, <CHARNAME>, je ferai ce que je dois faire, même si cela "
"signifie me battre pour Mélissane."

#: the_five.tra:616
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I was going to resurrect them anyway, to serve as my conquering avatars.  "
#| "And I prefer them far better this way... completely servile, obeying every "
#| "order without question."
msgid ""
"I was going to resurrect them anyway, to serve as my conquering avatars. And"
" I prefer them far better this way... completely servile, obeying every "
"order without question."
msgstr ""
"J'allais les ressusciter de toute façon, pour qu'ils servent en tant "
"qu'avatars. Et je les préfère bien mieux ainsi... complètement serviles, "
"obéissant à chaque ordre sans objection."

#: the_five.tra:617
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And since you recruited Balthazar to your side, I've decided on the "
#| "delicious irony of re-creating poor, pathetic Gromnir as well.  It delights "
#| "me to no end to know that he was right about me all along... and yet it made"
#| " no difference.  You murdered him still, as I knew you would."
msgid ""
"And since you recruited Balthazar to your side, I've decided on the "
"delicious irony of re-creating poor, pathetic Gromnir as well. It delights "
"me to no end to know that he was right about me all along... and yet it made"
" no difference. You murdered him still, as I knew you would."
msgstr ""
"Et puisque tu as recruté Balthazar, j'ai décidé par une subtile ironie de "
"recréer ce pauvre et pathétique Gromnir. Ca me fait plaisir de le voir "
"réaliser qu'il avait raison à mon sujet depuis le début... et ça n'a fait "
"aucune différence. Tu l'as tué aussi, comme je savais que tu le ferais."

#: the_five.tra:618
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You should have kept your energies to yourself, Melissan.  Spending them on "
#| "re-creating the Five will cost you... and cost you dearly."
msgid ""
"You should have kept your energies to yourself, Melissan. Spending them on "
"re-creating the Five will cost you... and cost you dearly."
msgstr ""
"Tu aurais mieux fait de gardr tes énergies pour toi, Mélissane. Les "
"gaspiller en recréant la Main va te coûter cher."

#: the_five.tra:619
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps.  But already I am immortal, which means I cannot be killed even by "
#| "you.  And there is still more of your father's essence for me to take."
msgid ""
"Perhaps. But already I am immortal, which means I cannot be killed even by "
"you. And there is still more of your father's essence for me to take."
msgstr ""
"Peut-être. Mais je suis déjà immortelle, ce qui signifie que nul ne peut me "
"tuer, pas même toi. Et il reste encore beaucoup de l'essence de ton père à "
"prendre."

#: the_five.tra:620
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "They provided a considerable challenge for you individually, <CHARNAME>.  I "
#| "wonder how you will fare against them all?"
msgid ""
"They provided a considerable challenge for you individually, <CHARNAME>. I "
"wonder how you will fare against them all?"
msgstr ""
"Ils t'ont causé beaucoup de problèmes individuellement, <CHARNAME>. Je me "
"demande comment tu vas faire pour les affronter tous en même temps ?"

#: the_five.tra:621
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So come, <CHARNAME>...kill your siblings once again.  If you can."
msgid "So come, <CHARNAME>...kill your siblings once again. If you can."
msgstr ""
"Viens, <CHARNAME>... tue tes frères et soeurs une fois de plus. Si tu le "
"peux."

#: the_five.tra:622
msgid "There is enough essence, in fact, even for you... Sarevok."
msgstr "Il y a assez d'essence en fait, même pour toi... Sarevok."

#: the_five.tra:623
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "But... we don't have all your siblings accounted for just quite yet, do we?"
#| "  Haven't you forgotten someone?"
msgid ""
"But... we don't have all your siblings accounted for just quite yet, do we? "
"Haven't you forgotten someone?"
msgstr ""
"Mais... nous n'avons pas tous tes frères et soeurs réunis encore ? N'avons-"
"nous pas oublié quelqu'un ?"

#: the_five.tra:624
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Oh, but we do, Sarevok.  I made you an offer once before, and that offer "
#| "still stands.  Join me now, abandon this pathetic whelp, and take your place"
#| " at my side."
msgid ""
"Oh, but we do, Sarevok. I made you an offer once before, and that offer "
"still stands. Join me now, abandon this pathetic whelp, and take your place "
"at my side."
msgstr ""
"Oh, mais si, Sarevok. Je t'ai fait une offre il ya longtemps, et cette offre"
" tient toujours. Rejoins-moi maintenant, abandonne cet être pathétique et "
"prends ta place à mes côtés."

#: the_five.tra:625
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The geas the fool placed on your heart is nothing.  I could easily remove "
#| "it.  In fact, I do so now.  There... act as you will."
msgid ""
"The geas the fool placed on your heart is nothing. I could easily remove it."
" In fact, I do so now. There... act as you will."
msgstr ""
"Le serment que cet idiot t'a imposé n'est rien. Je peux facilement le "
"briser. En fait, je viens de le faire. Maintenant, fais ce que tu veux."

#: the_five.tra:626
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Perhaps.  But you are a great warrior... and could be a fine general to lead"
#| " my earthly armies.  Power, riches, respect... all you desire.  Including "
#| "the return of the Bhaalspawn essence you lost.  Come, Sarevok... be the "
#| "demon you once were.  Serve me."
msgid ""
"Perhaps. But you are a great warrior... and could be a fine general to lead "
"my earthly armies. Power, riches, respect... all you desire. Including the "
"return of the Bhaalspawn essence you lost. Come, Sarevok... be the demon you"
" once were. Serve me."
msgstr ""
"Peut-être. Mais tu es un grand guerrier... et tu pourrais être un bon "
"général pour commander mes armées. Le pouvoir, la richesse, le respect... "
"tout ce que tu désires. Et également le retour de l'essence de Bhaal que tu "
"as perdue. Viens Sarevok, sois à nouveau le démon que tu étais. Sers-moi."

#: the_five.tra:627
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then fight for me you shall!  And your first victim will be the "
#| "<PRO_BROTHERSISTER> upon whom vengeance is so richly deserved!"
msgid ""
"Then fight for me you shall! And your first victim will be the "
"<PRO_BROTHERSISTER> upon whom vengeance is so richly deserved!"
msgstr ""
"Alors tu dois combattre pour moi ! Et ta première victime sera ton frère qui"
" ne mérite rien d'autre que ta vengeance !"

#: the_five.tra:628
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Then die with your fool <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, if that is your wish!  The Five"
#| " shall be the end of you both!"
msgid ""
"Then die with your fool <PRO_BROTHERSISTER>, if that is your wish! The Five "
"shall be the end of you both!"
msgstr ""
"Alors meurs aux côtés de ton frère, si c'est ce que tu veux ! La Main sera "
"votre fin à tous !"

#: the_five.tra:629
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I brought you here, Sarevok.  To give you a second chance.  Join me and "
#| "fight against <CHARNAME> and I will return the power you lost, the power you"
#| " crave so much.  I will make you the man you once were."
msgid ""
"I brought you here, Sarevok. To give you a second chance. Join me and fight "
"against <CHARNAME> and I will return the power you lost, the power you crave"
" so much. I will make you the man you once were."
msgstr ""
"Je t'ai fait venir ici, Sarevok. Pour te donner une seconde chance. Rejoins-"
"moi et combats <CHARNAME> et je te rendrai le pouvoir que tu as perdu, le "
"pouvoir que tu recherches tant. Je vais refaire de toi l'homme que tu étais."

#: the_five.tra:1008
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You are a fool, Melissan.  You should have kept what divine energy you had "
#| "for yourself and not spread it amongst such servants.  It will prove your "
